-- Generated from crystal_descriptions.pkl — run in the Supabase SQL editor.
insert into crystals (name, headline, description, star_sign, chakras) values
  ('Abalone (Paua Shell)', 'stone of patience', 'Abalone shell carries gentle yet deeply healing energy, guiding us toward emotional balance and inner clarity. It teaches patience and helps us look within for the answers we seek, fostering emotional control and self-understanding. As a powerful ally for chakra alignment, Abalone enhances awareness of both our inner strengths and vulnerabilities, encouraging growth through self-acceptance. It is also known for its connection to past life lessons, offering insight and integration of experiences beyond the present. Abalone’s calming influence supports the release of anxiety by helping us let go, allowing emotions to pass through us without overwhelming our system. Its soothing energy creates a sense of peace and resilience, making it especially beneficial during significant life transitions. Whether navigating the challenges of puberty or the shifts of menopause, Abalone brings stability, clarity, and a reminder of the strength that comes from within. It is a beautiful companion on the journey of emotional and spiritual healing.', 'Pisces, Cancer, Aquarius, and Scorpio', 'the crown, third eye and heart chakras'),
  ('Actinolite', 'Stone of protection from negative energies', 'Actinolite is a spiritually potent stone known for its grounding, protective, and transformational qualities. It serves as a bridge between the physical and spiritual realms, helping to align the body with higher consciousness and deeper insight. Actinolite is especially supportive during times of personal transformation, encouraging the release of old patterns, emotional wounds, and negative attachments. This allows for profound inner healing and growth.

Emotionally and mentally, Actinolite enhances self-awareness, mental clarity, and the courage to face inner truths. It promotes honesty with oneself and supports emotional resilience. As a powerful auric cleanser, it helps to protect the energy field from psychic disturbances and external negativity.

Resonating with the heart chakra, Actinolite inspires compassion and emotional balance, making it an ideal stone for those experiencing life transitions. Whether you are healing, evolving, or seeking inner peace, Actinolite offers a steady, supportive energy that gently guides the soul toward higher purpose and spiritual alignment.', 'Scorpio', 'Heart'),
  ('Adamite', 'A stone of enhancing the solar plexus and heart chakras', 'Adamite is a stone that enhances the solar plexus and heart chakras, aligning them together. By doing so, the Will is able to synergize with feelings released from the heart, exposing wants and desires while finding ways to pursue those said dreams. Adamite helps users get that “fire” relit inside of you, producing determination and optimism for one to achieve their desired destiny.', 'cancer', 'heart and solar plexus'),
  ('Aegirine', 'A stone of mental health and protection', 'Aegirine is a healing stone and will greatly improve one''s mental health. It will assist in breaking you out of tireless daily routines that are filled with negativity, and push you towards focusing on yourself. For anyone who is struggling with addiction of any sorts, Aegirine will bring out the strength from deep within that may have been buried beneath internal imbalances. There are a lot of stones that work well with Aegirine, one such being Moldavite. The strength of both these stones activates and aligns all chakras and is extremely powerful in banishing negative energies and entities. Aegirine can also be found within Nebula Stone, along with a combination of other minerals. Using Aegirine and Nebula crystals together will combine their powers with endless limitations.', 'tarus, pisces', 'all seven'),
  ('African Turquoise', 'stone for gain inner peace and maintain physical health', 'As it’s name indicates, African Turquoise is mined in Africa. This spotted teal gemstone is actually a Jasper, in the Chalcedony family. African Turquoise contains crystal Quartz, copper, and Iron which gives it an opaque appearance and a beautiful mottled colour.

African Turquoise is known as the stone of evolution, bringing about change and renewal. As with Turquoise, this gemstone is protective, opens intuition and assists in communication. 

African Turquoise can help one to find their right path and aids with depression, giving its wearer a more positive outlook on life. 

African turquoise help ease mood swings, encourage acceptance and sooth feelings of emotional aggravation. Also a stone to help with joint discomfort while helping bring lubrication within the joints and improved flexibility overall, it is also beneficial to kidney function and aids digestion.​', 'Cancer, Capricorn', 'Third Eye'),
  ('Agate', 'Stone for rebalancing and harmonising body, mind and spirit', 'Emotionally, Agate is a glorious gift for upping your self-confidence. For those who struggle with decision making or who tend to sit on the fence, Agate can encourage you to tap into your own deep well of intuition, to connect with your sense of knowledge, and to look inwards for the answers rather than to external forces. Agate stones are often crystals of strength and courage, they enhance our mental functions, they keep us sharp of mind and clear of heart, and they invite us to turn up the dial on our analytical abilities when it comes to sifting through problems. Unlike some of the dreamier and elevated crystals, Agate is more about giving you a great base in reality and ensuring that you stay balanced in your thinking. These traits can be enormously helpful, especially when it comes to giving you a sense of grounding so that you always feel safe and secure in your own being. For those who want to root in when it comes to their own soul and who are ready to let go of trauma and embrace their own brave truth, Agate gives you all that you need.', 'Gemini, Scorpio, Capricorn', 'All'),
  ('Apricot Agate', 'stone for calmness of mind and relieve distress', 'Apricot agate is a beautiful form of chalcedony that naturally forms in layered bands of colour, often filling cavities in lava where stunning crystal formations can appear. When dyed and polished, Agate geodes display striking, random colour patterns that make each piece unique. Naturally occurring in a variety of colours, each type of Agate carries its own subtle energetic vibration. It is known as a powerful balancing stone, harmonising yin and yang energies and promoting overall healing. Agate bridges the physical and etheric bodies, encouraging truth, courage, and emotional resilience. It can lift low moods and gently open the door to greater understanding. Physically, it supports the lymphatic system, pancreas, and circulation by grounding energies through the heart chakra. Apricot Agate, in particular, is gentle and protective, especially beneficial for children and teens. It soothes emotional distress and calms chaotic thoughts, making it a wonderful companion during hormonal changes or overwhelming life transitions..', 'Gemini', 'Root, Sacral, Solar Plexus, and Heart Chakras'),
  ('Black Agate', 'stone for inner strength', 'Black Agate, a variety of chalcedony, naturally forms in beautifully banded layers, often found filling cavities in lava where crystals may also grow. Sometimes dyed for visual impact, cut and polished Black Agate geodes display striking patterns that enhance their beauty and uniqueness. Each colour variation of Agate carries its own subtle vibration, but all are known for their harmonising properties. Black Agate, in particular, is a grounding stone that balances yin-yang energy and promotes overall healing. It bridges the physical and etheric bodies, helping one access inner truth and courage. Emotionally, it supports the release of depression and brings clarity through understanding. It also benefits the lymphatic system, pancreas, and circulatory system by stabilising the aura and grounding energy from the heart chakra downward. A simple practice involves holding different Agates in each hand—such as Green and Black Agate—and noting how the sensations differ. Over time, this builds a personalised healing toolkit.', 'Gemini', 'Root'),
  ('Blue Banded Agate', 'great nurturing and supportive stone', 'Blue banded agate is a form of chalcedony which naturally forms in bands of beautiful colours. It occurs as a cavity filling in lava and can often have wonderful crystals growing inside. An Agate Geode, immersed in dye before cutting, produces random absorption of colour. When they are cut and polished the finished product looks spectacular.



There are many natural colours of Agate, each having a slightly different vibration. Agate provides for the balancing of yin-yang energy and is therefore a good overall healing stone that brings balance to all parts of the body. It is a stone that helps create a bridge between the physical and the etheric bodies, seeking truth and courage within. It can aid in lifting depression by opening the door to understanding. It is both energising and grounding. The lymphatic system, the pancreas and the circulatory system all benefit from this mineral by stabilising the aura from the heart chakra downward, grounding dysfunctional energies.', 'Gemini', 'throat chakra'),
  ('Blue Lace Agate', 'great nurturing and supportive stone', 'Blue Agate is a form of chalcedony that naturally forms in beautiful, banded layers, often found filling lava cavities where crystals may grow. When Agate geodes are immersed in dye before cutting, they absorb colour in unique patterns, resulting in stunning polished pieces. While Agate occurs in many natural colours—each with its own vibration—it is universally known for balancing yin-yang energy and bringing harmony to the body and mind. A grounding and energising stone, Agate bridges the physical and etheric realms, supporting emotional healing, inner truth, and courage. Physically, it stabilises the aura and supports the lymphatic, pancreatic, and circulatory systems. Blue Agate, distinguished by its delicate blue and white banding, is particularly soothing. It strengthens the skeletal system and is often used for conditions like arthritis and joint issues. Spiritually, it activates higher chakras, especially the third eye and crown, encouraging mindfulness and connection. Colour-enhanced, it amplifies Agate’s core healing qualities.', 'Gemini', 'throat'),
  ('Green Agate', 'stone of  balance and luck', '(Green Agate) A form of chalcedony which naturally forms in bands of beautiful colours. It occurs as a cavity filling in lava and can often have wonderful crystals growing inside. An Agate Geode, immersed in dye before cutting, produces random absorption of colour. When they are cut and polished the finished product looks spectacular.



There are many natural colours of Agate, each having a slightly different vibration. Agate provides for the balancing of yin-yang energy and is therefore a good overall healing stone that brings balance to all parts of the body. It is a stone that helps create a bridge between the physical and the etheric bodies, seeking truth and courage within. It can aid in lifting depression by opening the door to understanding. It is both energising and grounding. The lymphatic system, the pancreas and the circulatory system all benefit from this mineral by stabilising the aura from the heart chakra downward, grounding dysfunctional energies.

Green Agate is wonderful for activating the chakras from the heart chakra down. It can ground and balance the auric field giving stability and balance. It is believed to reduce frustration and slow the metabolism, calming anger and agitation.', 'Gemini, Virgo', 'sacral'),
  ('Moss Agate', 'good luck stone', 'Moss agate is associated with the healing and survival of the plant kingdom and so many herbalists and Earth workers are drawn to this mineral. It opens the awareness to the ecology of our beautiful planet which explains the type of person naturally drawn to this crystal.



It aids creativity, stimulates the mind and memory, working at its best at the onset of any sign of memory loss or damage.  This is because it works as a catalyst for sparking memory associated routes to situations or events, a bit like a way finder or map as to where to find the information in the memory.

It works to help retrieval through one’s mind map.  It is most effective for memory problems with Moonstone.', 'Gemini', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Botswana Agate', 'A Stone of strengthening and stabilising', 'is a comfort stone, beneficial in overcoming depression, and strengthening during a grieving process. It helps alleviate obsessive thoughts and destructive mental patterns, and assists in overcoming fears, such as agoraphobia and panic attacks in crowded places. It’s considered as royalty in the Agate family', 'Gemini and scorpio', 'root, sarcal'),
  ('Crazy Lace Agate', 'A stone of mental agility, liveliness and variety, and encourages flexibility in thinking and action', 'Crazy Lace Agate is called the Laughter Stone, or “Happy Lace.” It is associated with sunny Mexican fiestas and dancing, and brings joy to those who wear it.  It is not a stone of protection, but of support and encouragement, elevating thoughts and promoting optimism. Its graceful design, in random lacy patterns, creates a circular flow of energy, stimulating for the mind and attitude', 'Virgo, Pisces, Gemini, Libra', 'Third eye, and crown'),
  ('Ellensburg Blue Agate', 'Stone for instilling compassion and forgiveness', '“Ellensburg Blue agates can enhance one’s stature and bring happiness through self understanding. It provides the energy to allow one to fully appreciate one’s abilities, characteristics and situations. It is useful for opening and activating the throat chakra. It provides assistance in communication and speech. Ellensburg Blue agate has been used in the treatment of disorders of the throat and to improve eyes”.

Even though blue agates can be found around the world the Ellensburg Blue agates hold a special place because of their rarity and beauty. Top quality Ellensburg Blue agates are sold by the carat for hundreds of dollars.', 'Gemini', 'Throat, Heart'),
  ('Geode Agate', 'stone of courage, emotional strength, self-confidence', 'Agate are said to be especially useful for protecting children from falling and hurting themselves. Emotionally, agate gives us courage, emotional strength, self-confidence and dispels fears. It can also lessen feelings of envy by grounding the emotions. In the same way, it assists with acceptance of all things.', 'Gemini', 'All 7 Chakras'),
  ('Laguna Agate', 'A stone of inner stability, composure, and maturity', 'Metaphysically, Agate has a lower intensity and vibrates to a slower frequency than other stones, but is highly regarded as a stabilizing and strengthening influence. Fiery Agates, like Laguna Agate, provide a steady, vibrant energy that stimulates a zest for living. They awaken the lower chakras and light the inner fires of Life Force, creativity, and sexuality.', 'Gemini', 'Root'),
  ('Lake Superior Agate', 'A stone of physical healing, espcially the respiratory and digestive', 'Is a positive, supportive stone for those who are going through change in their life. A stone of transformation, Lake Superior Agate will help you to stay stable and secure. Agate is a wonderful gemstone for balancing the mind, body, and spirit as well as helping you to slow down and center yourself. It transforms negative energy into positive energy. Agate enhances mental function, improves concentration, enhances perception and analytical abilities. ... Agate instills security and safety.', 'Gemini', 'root'),
  ('Peach Agate', 'A stone of self acceptance and healing', 'Helps heal and balance the Sacral Chakra. It has a gentle, nurturing energy that can quietly boost your creativity and help initiate transformation in your life.', 'Aries, Leo, Sagitarius', 'Sacral'),
  ('Plume Agate', 'A stone for vision - useful in meditation', 'Plume Agate is specifically known to help in making important decisions in life. As a powerful stone Agate is also known to help accept one''s own truth and build self-confidence. It also encourages a wearer to speak the truth. The stone helps one steer away from negativity and ill-will.', 'Gemini', 'all'),
  ('Snakeskin Agate', 'A stone for strength', 'promotes strength and perseverance during times of turmoil. ... With its snake like appearance, Snakeskin Agate is believed to help us initiate the movement of Kundalini energy through our Charkas out through the Crown bringing the spiritual enlightenment we seek.', 'Scorpio', 'root, solar plexus, and crown chakras.'),
  ('Turritella Agate', 'A stone for ancestral connection', 'Turritella Agate is a spiritual crystal, deeply connected to the earth and home, to one''s personal roots and ancestry, even the events of one''s past. It is a survival stone, one of strength and protection. Ancient life held within its form lends the power of wisdom and healing.', 'Gemini, Cancer, Aquarius', 'earth star and root chakras'),
  ('Dendritic Agate', 'A stone for healing and balancing', 'Dendritic Agate is a deeply grounding stone that fosters a connection to nature and encourages acceptance of one’s roots and life journey. Often associated with stability and inner peace, it helps align us with the natural flow of the universe, making it especially useful during times of change. Dendritic Agate supports emotional resilience, reminding us to embrace transitions calmly and with grace.

Spiritually, it provides positive energy for self-healing and the development of intuitive or psychic abilities. It can also help bring forward memories or insights from the past that are relevant to present growth. Used in meditation or placed under a pillow, it may stimulate dreams and recollection of past lives.

Known for its healing properties, Dendritic Agate enhances concentration, strengthens memory, and is often used to support learning. Physically, it''s believed to assist with blood-related conditions, hormonal balance, nervous system disorders, insomnia, and detoxification, making it a valuable all-round healing stone.', 'Gemini', 'root chakra'),
  ('Fire Agate', 'A stone to dispel fear', 'Fire Agate represents the spiritual flame of absolute perfection, dispelling fear at the deepest level of the inner being.', 'Aries, Leo, Sagittarius', 'root and sacral chakra'),
  ('Holly Blue Agate', 'A stone for healing', 'Holly Blue agate is a stone that is as beautiful as it is healing. A good use of Holley Blue would be to help you accept situations in your life that you cannot control. Physically Ithis stone to lesson the pain of ''stress'' headaches and to relax stiff muscles.

Holly Blue Agate is a mentally calming stone. This is a good stone for the crown chakra, stimulating and connecting it with the heart and third eye chakras. This increases intuition and spiritual insight. 

Use Holly Blue Agate to help you release emotional traumas and blockages. This stone will help you find positives and lessons in every situation.', 'Virgo', 'crown, third eye heart'),
  ('Agnitite', 'A stone to hareness collective energy', 'The currents of Agnitite are powerful and often make the body feel warm or even hot. They tend to enter through the crown chakra, working their way down to the heart, and flowing from there throughout the body. Agnitite stimulates the entire liquid crystal body matrix, and helps the body learn to resonate in vibrational unity. It can enhance qualities such as intuition, healing, strength of will, a sense of ones purpose, and awareness of one’s shared consciousness with that of the world at large. For spiritual self healing agnitite is recommended to those wishing to purify the blood and cellular tissues. It can act as a detoxifying influence at the same time it energizes all of one’s system', '', 'root and earth star'),
  ('Ajoite', 'A stone of powerful feminie energy', 'Ajoite will help you connect to the angelic realm. It will connect you to the Divine and bring forth a deeper knowledge and understanding that you can share with others.', 'virgo', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Amazonite', 'A stone of peace, truth, harmony, and communication.', 'Amazonite is a stone that can help you speak the truth, speak with confidence and help communicate harmoniously. Wear on days where you have to give speeches or prepare for meetings. It’s also great for balancing male and female energies.', 'virgo', 'throat, heart, polar plexus'),
  ('Amber', 'Botanic resin', 'The energies of this stone will help you evolve spiritually. It’s a terrific aid that you can use in your meditation because it will allow you to connect to your higher self.', 'leo, libra, aquarius', 'throat, solar plexus, scaral'),
  ('Amethyst', 'stone of sacral kingship, virility and prosperity', 'Main component of amethyst are silica, hardness 7, specific gravity 2.65, and refractive index 1.54-1.55.

Viewed from different angles, natural amethysts show a beautiful purple tone with a little blue or red, due to such minerals as iron and manganese. We can also find amethysts in lilac, red, crimson and light or dark purple, among which dark purple and red are the best.

Amethysts usually have natural ice cracks or white impurities too, produced in volcanic, pegmatite, limestone or shale caves.

Amethysts are widely distributed in nature, and the main production areas include Brazil, Russia, South Africa, and Madagascar.', 'Aquarius', 'crown'),
  ('Amethyst – Vera Cruz', 'stone of spiritual ascension and growth', 'Vera Cruz Amethyst crystals have amazing luster and clarity. They run from a very light shade of lavender through to the very rare rich deep purple color. They can form with a variety of attributes such as phantoms, single and double terminated points, as well as in cluster form. And on rare occasions, as enhydro – which are crystals with moving water bubbles inside them. Over time, the miners in the Vera Cruz region have learned to really take care of these special crystals through their birthing process, so it is quite possible to get these crystals in undamaged form, especially the specimens our retail arm Majestic Quartz has in stock – we deal direct with the mines.', 'Pisces. Aquarius, Aries, Capricorn (ancient)', 'All'),
  ('Amethyst Clusters', 'Stone for emotional and spiritual protection', 'Amethyst Clusters make powerful visualization assistants and help to manifest these visualizations into 3D reality! Amethyst Clusters throw out their beautiful healing energy all around your home. They are great tools to be placed in the center of group meditations. Amethyst Clusters also make for excellent cleansing and charging stations for other crystals. When placed beside one’s head, they are very good for drawing out EMF style radiation that generally gets stored in that part of the human body. Amethyst likes to be cleansed in water/saltwater and earth.', 'Aquarius, Pisces', 'Third Eye'),
  ('Amethyst Flowers', 'Stone  for spiritual clarity, divine peace, and uncovering your inherent wisdom.', 'Amethyst Flowers Properties and Meaning – Amethyst flowers are groups of Amethyst crystals grouped together to form the shape of a flower. They are quite rare and special. Amethyst Flowers for spiritual clarity, divine peace, and uncovering your inherent wisdom.', 'Aquarius, Pisces and Sagittarius', 'Third Eye'),
  ('Ametrine', 'A stone of balance and connection', 'As a stone of both balance and connection, ametrine is believed to relieve tension, bring serenity and stimulate creativity, as well as balance mental stability and self-confidence. Ametrine is considered a double boost to remove toxins from the body, as both amethyst and citrine are detoxifiers.', 'Libra', 'Third eye'),
  ('Ammonite', 'Stone of Personal Growth', '​Ammonite will bring about a circulation of energy, making you feel more stable, protected, and grounded in your life. Its energies will provide you with a kind of stability that’s dynamic.
​Ammolite is a stone that will convert all your energies that you receive into love and positivity. This stone will deepen your meditative experience, enhance your moods, relieve any kind of trauma, and boost your stamina.', 'Capricorn, Virgo', 'root,sacral'),
  ('Amphibole Quartz', 'Stone for peace, harmony and serenity', 'Amphibole Quartz Properties and Meaning – Amphibole Quartz Crystals have inclusions, mostly consisting of (yellow) Limonite, (red) Hematite, (white) Kaolinite, and (pink) Lithium. This Quartz is from Bahia, Brazil.', 'Pisces', 'Third Eye and Crown Chakras'),
  ('Anandalite (Aurora or Rainbow Quartz)', 'Stone of psychic awakening', 'Anandalite, a powerful form of quartz, is known for its striking beauty and exceptionally high healing energy. Also called Iris Quartz or Anadolyte, its official name, "Anandalite," translates to "divine bliss," reflecting its deep spiritual resonance. The crystal’s vibrations are strong and intense, making it a prominent presence in any space. Anandalite is often used as a tool to communicate with the divine, offering a pathway to spiritual enlightenment and bliss.

One of the crystal’s most important qualities is its ability to promote emotional, physical, and spiritual healing. Whether you''re seeking to heal from emotional wounds or regain faith, Anandalite’s energy can help restore balance and peace. It is especially effective in working with the heart chakra, where it facilitates deep emotional healing and connection. Holding Anandalite allows its powerful vibrations to flow through the body, helping to elevate your energy and bring about profound transformation.', 'Cancer and leo', 'heart'),
  ('Ancestralite', 'stone of  balance for the mind, body, and soul', 'Anandalite is a stunning quartz crystal known for its exceptional healing energy and vibrant beauty. Also referred to as Iris Quartz or Anadolyte, its name, "Anandalite," translates to "divine bliss," which reflects its powerful spiritual resonance. The crystal’s intense vibrations make it highly noticeable in any environment, offering a strong connection to higher realms and spiritual enlightenment.

This crystal is especially valued for its ability to aid emotional, physical, and spiritual healing. It helps heal emotional wounds, restore faith, and bring balance to the body and mind. Anandalite is particularly effective in working with the heart chakra, promoting deep emotional healing and a sense of inner peace. When held, the crystal’s energy flows through the body, raising vibrations and creating a transformative, uplifting experience. Anandalite is an ideal stone for anyone seeking a profound spiritual shift or a boost to their emotional and physical well-being.', 'Gemini', 'root chakra'),
  ('Angel Aura quartz', 'Stone of happiness, joy and uplifting enegry', 'Angel Aura Quartz is an extremely high vibrational stone that’s energies can be felt to the touch, no matter the sensitivity of a person. This magic mineral can provide enough energy to fill environments with endless rays of joy, happiness, and uplifting energy. Angel Aura Quartz is the perfect stone to help when one may feel emotionally unstable or distressed. The energies that radiate from this stone provide a protective shield around ones aura that helps provide inner peace, mental clarity, highented intellect, and pure serenity. This stone is here to provide these energies on the worst of days to get your emotional body in check, while clearing up the mind of the daily mental fog. Angel Aura Quartz will assist in the complete evaluation and transformation of ones current life, and push one to take action and do what they truly love. This powerful crystal will help keep one''s goals and dreams in check, and help in providing a pathway to those dreams. Nothing in this world is out of your reach, and Angel Aura Quartz should be a daily reminder of that.', 'Aries', 'Etheric, and crown'),
  ('Angelinite', 'stone of guidance', 'Lemurian Aquatine Calcite, with its soothing pale to deep blue/green hues, embodies the gentle qualities of calming and sensitive crystals. When held, it enhances the dream-state and facilitates access to theta consciousness, the state between waking and subconscious. This state is ideal for daydreaming, lucid dreaming, hypnosis, and astral travel.

Setting an intention to connect with Lemuria and its ancient wisdom while holding Lemurian Aquatine Calcite can support exploration of lost knowledge and spiritual growth. It is particularly helpful for those beginning their spiritual awakening, offering guidance through the challenges of connecting with one''s spiritual self. Trusting that you are already spiritually awakened can be a powerful leap, and this crystal serves as a compassionate mentor.

When stroked along the body, Lemurian Aquatine Calcite has a cooling, calming effect on the emotional body, akin to a mother’s lullaby, providing soothing, peaceful energy that fosters emotional balance and tranquility.', 'Leo, Scorpio', 'Third Eye (Brow) Chakra, Crown Chakra'),
  ('Angelite', 'A stone of creating high vibration', 'Angelite is a very high vibrational stone that activates and aligns our throat, third eye, and crown chakras. This stone will help attune oneself to a higher frequency, which helps connect both their guardian angels and spirit guides. Using this stone as a meditation tool will help transmit and vocalize (into the physical plane) the knowledge in which you absorb through the third eye and crown connection. Angelite is a very powerful communication stone when it comes to connecting to other realms and frequencies. As you work with this stone repeatedly, you’ll notice your inner vision becoming more vivid. Your dreams will be easier to understand, allowing you to be more in touch with your psychic abilities and how to channel them.', 'Aquarius', 'crown, third eye, throat'),
  ('Anhydrite', 'stone of Communication with spirit guides, enhanced psychic abilities, self-acceptance and forgiveness', 'Anhydrite has a Lovely energy; calming, intuitive, strong and sensual. This mineral is a variety of garnet and comes in a wide range of colours. This mineral enhances and balances ones male energies so can be a marvellous addition to any medicine pouch. Great for confidence boosting and a tower of strength in difficult times.


Think of it like a guardian angel that can be called upon at any time to defend, protect and dispel fear.', 'Cancer, Pisces, and Scorpio', 'Throat, Third Eye and Crown'),
  ('Apache Tears', 'A stone for grief, grounding and protection', 'Apache Tears are not altered but are natural crystals that heal grief. They have a strong action to aid emotional healing and bring you comfort when you are grieving.', 'capricorn and aries', 'root chakra'),
  ('Apatite', 'stone for Intellect,Focus,Learning,Clarity of concentration, Peace and harmony,', 'Apatite is a stunning crystal, yet it often goes unnoticed and underappreciated in the healing community. Ask a dozen healers about its uses, and you''ll likely receive a variety of answers. As a result, it’s rare to find Apatite in most healing crystal pouches or therapy rooms.

Over the years, healers have discovered that Apatite is effective for clearing blockages across all chakras. It can quickly remove aura blockages, especially if they haven''t been present for long. More recently, it''s been recognized for its ability to clear long-standing emotional and mental blockages, including those carried through past lives.

If you find yourself repeatedly facing the same challenges or negative patterns, such as recurring relationship issues or self-doubt, Apatite can help release these stuck energies. Known for its persistence, Apatite works patiently to clear obstacles and facilitate healing. With its many colours, including blue/green, azure blue, and yellow-green, Apatite is a powerful tool for transformation and self-empowerment.', 'Gemini', 'solar plexus, throatt'),
  ('Apatite, Blue', 'Stone of psychic acvitation and access to knowledge', 'Blue Apatite is a stone of manifestation attuned to the future, activating psychic abilities and allowing expansion of knowledge. Apatite will stimulate the intellect and brings ideas from the mind down into the earth realm through realizations. ... Apatite has been known to also successfully suppress hunger.', 'Gemini, Libra', 'throat, third eye'),
  ('Apophyllite', 'A stone connected to the soul star to connect with higher relams', 'Apophyllite embodies the power of the self-less helper and can be used to promote acts of kindness and charity. Though it is always important to care for yourself, if you find yourself having difficulties giving yourself to others fully or committing to your friends and partners’ goals, Apophyllite can help open you up and provide you with more fluidity. Apophyllite also represents the power of the Soul Star, what some refer to as the eighth chakra. This chakra floats above the crown chakra, just above the head, and represents the home where your soul rests.

For this reason, Apophyllite can be very useful to meditate with for any occasion, but especially if you have any needs for becoming reconnected with a soul or a soul part such as during a healing soul retrieval ceremony or reconnection with your inner child. It can represent the transcendence of oneself above the dichotomy of the form in which you entered this world and your continued journey along the path of self-enlightenment.

Apophyllite will help enhance your intuition. The energies of this stone (like the energies of Amethyst) will make your senses sharper and your visions clearer in a way that you cannot help but acknowledge and trust them! It will help you become more sensitive to things, events, and people in your life. Your instincts will be usually right, and you will learn to trust them more and more over time. Apophyllite can also help you connect with your spirit guides and guardian angels.', 'Gemini, Libra', 'third eye, crown, heart and soma'),
  ('Green Apophyllite', 'A stone of love, brings peace harmony and abundance', 'Green Apophyllite crystals carry the energy of love. This crystal will bring peace, harmony, and abundance in your space as well. It can cleanse and balance the energy in your heart chakra.', 'Gemini, Libra', 'third eye, crown, heart and soma'),
  ('Apophyllite Stilbite', 'A stone of connecting with spirits and animals', 'Orange to yellow colors of Apophyllite shows the unique colors due to stilbite. It is seen in green colors too. Apophyllite stilbite is excellent for communicating with spirit guides and animals.', 'Gemini, Libra', 'third eye, crown, heart and soma'),
  ('Pink Apophyllite', 'A stone of connecting with the higher realms', 'Seen as a pink druzy stone with Rhodonite hues, pink apophyllites help you connect to the angelic realm, high above.', 'Gemini, Libra', 'third eye, crown, heart and soma'),
  ('Apophyllite Scolecite', 'A stone of protection', 'When Apophyllite forms at the tips of scolecite like a bouquet it is called Apophyllite scolecite. A rare stone, it is the best crystal for balance and stability as well as to ward of bad mojo!', 'Gemini, Libra', 'third eye, crown, heart and soma'),
  ('Aqua Aura Quartz', 'A stone to calm the emotions and emotional body', 'These quartz crystals have very powerful metaphysical properties, and this is partly due to the fact that they are quartz crystals. But it also relates to the layer of fine gold that covers the stone. These crystals resonate strongly with a vibration that is powerful to aid communication and psychic gifts. They have an excellent healing energy in the body, to cleanse and heal your auric field.

These stones are said to attract wealth and success, and are strong stones to aid your spiritual growth', 'Aquarius', 'All'),
  ('Aquamarine', 'Stone of pure communication', 'Aquamarine is a very special stone that helps in opening a clear channel between your heart and throat chakras. This ever so important connection allows one to constantly speak from the heart and to the highest truths. This beryl variety is a perfect stone to help aid you in the solving of conflicts, arguments and disagreements. Aquamarine can also support you in cooling those fiery emotions that desire to overtake us. The water element shines bright in this stone and urges us to peel back a layer of ourselves to allow that inner being to glow. In addition Aquamarine is here to help you constantly refresh your emotions and provide mental clarity. There are times when your heart will be completely open and clear, but yet your mind may tend to still be foggy. Aquamarine supports us in wisdom, intellect, knowledge, the enhancement of ideas, and clarity of the mind. When one’s open heart and clear mind are able to work in sync, the opportunities and relationships will become endless.', 'Aries, gemini and pisces', 'throat, heart'),
  ('Aragonite', 'Stone of grounding and balance', 'Aragonite has a highly grounding energy that will stabilize you as you bring inner balance and expand your awareness. This stone teaches us renewed strength and will help to focus the emotions on things that are most important to you. In today’s society, many people tend to dwell on what’s difficult and not realize the negativity that they are producing. Aragonite helps in balancing the heart with the mind, allowing the release of emotional bindings weighing on the heart. This strengthens you as a person and gives you the confidence to overcome any difficult situation involving anxiety or stress. Aragonite will bring emotional stability by assuring that whatever pain you are feeling will pass, empowering and encouraging you to use all of your energies constructively. This crystal will help clear the mind, boosting motivation and courage to give you the energy needed to meet your challenges. This is especially effective in situations where you feel like backing down or running away. Aragonite reminds us of our own strengths and capabilities, and shows us that we have the power to face whatever comes our way. Overall, Aragonite will help to cope emotionally, mentally, and physically. It’s a powerful emotional healing stone that brings a sense of peace and tranquility to a normally unrest mind. This stone encourages new beginnings and renewed relationships.', 'capricorn', 'all seven'),
  ('Arfvedsonite', 'stone for connection to the spirit world', 'ChatGPT said:
Arfvedsonite is a dynamic crystal known for its assertive energy and ability to take charge, pushing you to take control of your life. This stone is a true mover and shaker, creating synchronicities that align people and circumstances in perfect timing. It opens doors to extraordinary opportunities, but it’s up to you to recognize and seize these moments.

Arfvedsonite is excellent for breaking old patterns and removing them, though it’s important not to replace them with the same habits. It’s a comfort stone for times of displacement, such as starting university, being in the hospital, visiting family, or traveling unexpectedly.

For anyone seeking a fresh start, Arfvedsonite is a powerful ally. Use it as a tool to reshape your life, connect with your guides, and take risks. Sometimes, a leap of faith is the key to new beginnings—nothing ventured, nothing gained. This crystal is here to help you transform your life', 'Gemini', 'Third Eye and Throat Chakras'),
  ('Arkansas Quartz', 'Stone for its purity and energies', 'Arkansas Quartz Properties and Meaning – South Arkansas has a wide variety of Quartz crystals. There is plenty of styles and flavors for everyone to choose from or dig.', 'All', 'crown'),
  ('Atlantisite', 'stone of Love & Relationships', 'Atlantisite is a combination of Stichtite and Serpentine. This is a stone of deep healing and grounding. It enables us to activate our Kundalini energy to connect with our deepest self and life force. It is a wonderful stone to use when beginning a new relationship and residual, unsealed emotions and trauma that arise while we become vulnerable.

Atlantisite is associated with all seven Chakras of the body, most closely with the Crown and Heart Chakras. It is connected to the grounded pragmatism of Virgo and the romanticism of Libra.', 'pisces', 'Heart chakra'),
  ('Auralite', 'stone for instilling laser-sharp clarity and spiritual awareness', 'Auralite brings with it favour and protection from the angels, a crystal of divine blessings.


Energetically this crystal buzzes stronger than Super Seven and pushes through psychic blockages.

It can be used for astral travellings, for access to the Halls of Learning and Akashic Records.

Auralite pulls negativity away from the body and requires washing frequently to renenergise the crystal to work at its optimum.', 'Aquarius, Pisces', 'Cleanses and aligns all. Activates alta major, soul star, stellar gateway'),
  ('Autumn Jasper', 'stone for clear mind and enhance concentration', 'Autumn Jasper comes in a mottled warm brick red and avocado green show that reminds us of the Fall in the Boreal Forest. Imagine the red maple leaves and the green coniferous trees and a long leisurely walk through the forest. Helping release stresses and bringing your mind to the joy of the moment, being connected to nature, to Mother Earth.... this is Autumn Jasper. Let this gemstone clear your mind, enhance your concentration, ground and center you. The energy of Autumn Jasper brings tranquility, wholeness, and healing. A very nurturing gemstone, Autumn Jasper allows the wearer to release the mundane in order to embrace “joie de vivre”.', 'Scorpio, Sagittarius', 'Root, Sacral'),
  ('Avalon Stone', 'stone for detoxify negative energies', 'Avalon Stone, found in Glastonbury, features black and brown hues with occasional white inclusions. Formed from limestone and mudstone layers over 195 to 200 million years ago, it is a protective stone that absorbs negative energies, shielding you from harm, negativity, and emotional stress, especially when away from home.

Emotionally, Avalon Stone illuminates hidden fears, secrets, and insecurities, helping you become aware of deep, unresolved issues. As light enters these dark spaces, transformation occurs, signaling new beginnings.

This gentle stone aids in releasing emotional blockages and encourages self-awareness. Wearing Avalon Stone helps you recognize mood shifts, offering the space needed for healing. Imbued with the energy of Glastonbury, the heart chakra of the planet, it fosters emotional growth and self-acceptance.', 'Capricorn', 'Root'),
  ('Azeztulite', 'stone for  removing blockages and stagnant negative energies', 'Golden Azeztulite is a rare crystal that has a very strong, powerful, intense, focused energy as known as Healer''s Quartz or Himalayan Gold Azeztulite. Golden Azeztulite comes from the highest mountains in the world, the Himalayan Mountains. 

It cleanses all of the Chakras, removing blockages and stagnant negative energies. It also helps to remove entities that are attached to one''s energy fields. Golden Azuztulite carries the high vibrational energy of the Great Central Sun, the center of cosmos, the point of origin of all physical-spiritual creation. The Azez spoke about these stones as wonderful and beneficial gifts for those who are searching for light and universal love. These crystals have the stongest energetic links with the people of both Atlantis and Lemuria.', 'All', 'Crown'),
  ('Azumar', 'Stone of insight and communication', 'Azumar is a high-frequency stone known for its transformative and deeply soothing energy. It resonates with the water in our bodies, promoting cellular rejuvenation and emotional healing. Azumar calms the physical body, releases emotional tension, and uplifts the spirit, creating a profound sense of joy and peace.

This stone works with the Liquid Crystal Body Matrix, clearing negativity and emotional blockages such as fear, anger, and envy. In their place, it brings serenity, confidence, and a sense of being surrounded by love. Azumar’s energetic flow can dissolve dysfunctional patterns, helping to clarify consciousness and awaken intuitive gifts.

Many experience enhanced clairvoyance, telepathy, or visionary insight while working with Azumar. It is especially supportive for oracles, mediums, and anyone seeking deeper connection with Spirit. With its gentle yet powerful influence, Azumar becomes a catalyst for personal growth, emotional healing, and expanded awareness.', 'Cancer, libra, scorpio', 'heart, throat, third eye'),
  ('Azurite', 'Stone of psychic abilities', 'Azurite is a stone that activates and unlocks our third eye and crown chakras, thereby linking the two. It''s known as one of the premier stones when it comes to accessing our own psychic abilities. It can assist you with lucid dreaming, astral projection, intuitive meditation, insight, and inner vision. If one has many dreams and often wonders what they mean, then this is the perfect stone for you! Azurite can help enhance those very dreams and decode their imagery. Azurite will raise one''s mental awareness, intellect, and wisdom that can help you reach new goals and desires. This copper carbonate is all about the mind and will help in the cleansing and purging of negativity within it. Azurite brings with it great clarity that can help in the disposing of negative thoughts, bad habits, and even addictions.', 'Sagittarius', 'crown and third eye'),
  ('Azurite Malachite', 'stone forAnxiety Eased, Stability', 'Azurite Malachite Properties and Meaning – Azurite Malachite is a member of the Copper family. Azurite Malachite comes in both massive and crystalline form, with colors ranging from green to blue.', 'Capricorn', 'Heart, Solar Plexus'),
  ('Bird''s Eye Rhyolite', 'stone for possessing nurturing energies', 'This gemstone is found in Mexico, with its beautiful tones of greys, yellows, reds, and browns with swirls of patterns, Rhyolite brings a comforting knowledge that “everything is perfectly as it should be".  When you hold Bird’s Eye Rhyolite in your hands, you feel its cool comforting energies, opening the Throat and the Solar Plexus Chakras. A great go-to gemstone for those who need to find their voices and those with Solar Plexus blocked by emotions. A balancer of Yin Yang energies, brings tranquility and a feeling of wholeness. Birds’ Eye Rhyolite assists one to move forward on their journey, removing obstacles on ones’ path. It is a stone of protection, regeneration, and an overall healer.

All Jaspers are known as possessing nurturing energies, Birds’ Eye is no different, it strengthens during periods of stress and of spiritual growth. Physically, this gemstone grounds, supports the circulatory system, the digestive system, and the thyroid gland.', 'Saggitarius', 'Solar Plexus, Throat'),
  ('Bismuth', 'Stone of Stimulation', 'This element stimulates energy and vitality and can help you to achieve your goals, especially when working as part of a team. It can be used to support transformation by aiding travel between the physical plane and realms of astral and spirit. It can also help with visualisation while shamanic journeying. Bismuth aids in relieving feelings of overwhelm, isolation and loneliness.', 'aquarius', 'all seven'),
  ('Bixbite – Red Beryl', 'Stone for  Self Esteem Divine Love, Connection With the Angelic Realm', 'Bixbite – Red Beryl Properties and Meaning – Bixbite is a member of the Beryl family. It comes in crystalline form, with color ranging from pink to deep red. This mineral is rare.', 'Libra', 'Heart, Root'),
  ('Black Beryl', 'stone of  energy  protective and strong', 'Black Beryl is a rare and enigmatic crystal, newly discovered and still largely undocumented. Though part of the Beryl family—home to Aquamarine and Emerald—its deep black hue defies easy classification, with its exact coloring still a mystery. Energetically, Black Beryl is intensely grounding and protective, resonating with the energy of Black Tourmaline or Black Spinel. It supports inner work during emotionally challenging times, helping one face shadow aspects with honesty and strength.

Meditating with Black Beryl brings a deep sense of peace and surrender, like a spiritual reset. Its quiet power encourages stillness, presence, and acceptance—urging us to release the pressure of constant striving. For those feeling emotionally worn, this crystal offers relief and grounding. Its greatest lesson: let go, simply be, and allow the light to return.', 'Scorpio', 'Base'),
  ('Black Dioptase', 'stone for overcome addictions of all kinds and stress', 'A rare and expensive crystal, Dioptase is a very powerful crystal for the higher Heart Chakra. It carries the green rays that encourages compassion and forgiveness, filling the heart with joy and peace.  Meditating with Dioptase may bring up and heal issues from past life that may be holding you back. Thus, releasing Karma and helping you move on. Dioptase makes you a better listener in a relationship. It makes emotional subjects easier to abord. It’s a good stone to process information without letting your ego or your feelings get in the way. It also increases your partnership skills. Dioptase is primarily used as a talisman, opens the Third Eye and activates the spiritual alignment and psychic abilities. 

Dioptase is excellent to prevent heart attacks and heals heart conditions. Most addictions stem from the Heart Chakra, Dioptase can help you overcome addictions of all kinds and stress.', 'Capricorn, Virgo, Taurus', 'Heart, Third Eye, Crown'),
  ('Black Obsidian', 'Stone of protection, grounding and spiritual communication', 'Known as a “psychic vacuum cleaner”, Black Obsidian gets rid of all the junk and cleanses all negativity out of your auric field and environment. This stone has powerful grounding frequencies and will heavily assist in psychic protection when needed. Obsidian also brings out all of our creative energies so that they may be intertwined and influence our every action. As humans, it’s important to constinalty be using our creative energies to keep them free-flowing at ease. When we reduce our output of creativity, these energies begin to go dormant as if they will never be needed again. It’s very hard to re-ignite certain creative energies so it is best to constantly be using them.', 'Scorpio, sagittarius', 'root'),
  ('Black Onyx', 'stone of happiness, good fortune and inner strength', 'Found in many countries, Onyx primarily refers to the parallel banded variety of the silicate mineral chalcedony. Agate and onyx are both varieties of layered chalcedony that differ only in the form of the bands: agate has curved bands and onyx has parallel bands. The colours of its bands range from black to almost every colour.', 'Leo', 'Root'),
  ('Black Tourmaline', 'Stone of Protection', 'Black Tourmaline is a powerful stone that can be used to protect against any kind of negative influence. It''s considered one of the best stones to protect agains harmful EMFs. During stressful times can be used to regain emotional balance and stability.', 'Libra', 'Root'),
  ('Bloodstone', 'Stone of energy', 'Called the Sun Stone, and later Christ’s Stone, its energy carries the purity of blood and inherently speaks of life and birth, vitality and strength, passion and courage. As a talisman it is both mystical and magical, and its virtues are protective and nurturing. Wear or carry Bloodstone to increase mental clarity and to aid in decision-making. It provides a mental boost when motivation is lacking, and can revitalize the mind and body if you are exhausted. Bloodstone stimulates dreaming and heightens intuition. It is marvelous for increasing creativity and cultivating a project from the idea stage through to actualization. It encourages blessings and prosperity.', 'Aries', 'root, sacral, solar plexus, heart'),
  ('Blue Adventurine', 'Stone of psychic activator and helps one open up their third eye (pineal gland)', 'Blue Aventurine is a psychic activator and helps one open up their third eye (pineal gland). This process doesn’t just happen overnight, as one must work with this stone repeatedly in order to fully tap into its interdimensional potential. Place this stone over your third eye during deep meditation sessions and you will begin to feel a tingling sensation. This effect will start at your forehead and slowly begin to imbue your whole body. The energy you are experiencing during this time is here to help relax your physical body while elevating your consciousness to new heights. As one’s spirit learns to ascend, the pathway to your higher being begins to be laid out before you. The journey must begin with you, however, Blue Aventurine is here to assist, specifically focusing on enhancing your mental behavior.', 'Aries', 'heart'),
  ('Blue Beryl', 'stone for de-stress', 'An excellent de-stresser, Blue Beryl is a gentle gemstone that helps you shed old belief systems that no longer serve you.  Blue Beryl instills calmness and stillness, if your life is stressful, let this gemstone work with you.

Assists in communication, encourages a positive viewpoint, helps calm distractions, enhances courage, calms overstimulated emotions. Making it a great stone for those with ADD/ADHD.

Beryl is available in different colours; pink (Morganite), green, red (Bixbite). Blue Beryl supports the pulmonary and circulatory systems, liver, heart, stomach, spine, and throat. 

A Third Eye opener, Blue Beryl assist one reach a deep meditative space for expanding and merging with the light.', 'Leo', 'Solar Plexus, Third Eye, Crown'),
  ('Blue Goldstone', 'A stone  for empaths', 'Blue Goldstone is highly regarded in the spirit realm as a protection mineral. It is the stone of confidence and ambition, encouraging motivation and drive. It has a positive energy, which makes it an uplifting stone while also promoting vitality', 'Sagittarius', 'Throat, heart and crown'),
  ('Blue John fluorite', 'stone of ancient wisdom and knowledge', 'Blue John is an excellent emotional healer as it releases emotions of angst and jealousy replacing them with rational feelings of stability.

We find that our healers and followers say that Blue John is the go too mineral when you need to give yourself a good talking too. It is great for introspection and the analytical evaluation of a situation.

We believe that having and working with a piece of this mineral brings about the energy of ‘change your prospective and change your life’.

Full of ancient wisdom and knowledge Blue John can be used or even programmed to be used to protect one’s auric field. This is very useful allowing thinking and processing space that is uncontaminated by the power of another’s influence.

Blue John when used in this way makes a great positive motivator and a great addition to a positive motivation medicine pouch.', 'Pisces', 'third eye, crown'),
  ('Blue Obsidian', 'stone of protection for sensitive or psychic people', 'Blue Obsidian cannot be used for negative works. This is the protection stone for sensitive or psychic people. It provides a great defense against negative psychic energy and also gives one a general sense of calm and well being. Blue Obsidian, on top of having the general properties of Obsidian, it also stimulates the throat chakra. An excellent stone for someone who has to speak in public, since it enhances communication. It is said to aid telepathic skills and astral travel. Blue Obsidian also acts as a protector during traveling. This gemstone should be used for psychic defence.', 'Pisces', 'Throat, solar plexus'),
  ('Blue Tiger’s Eye', 'stone of intuition and insight', 'Chatoyancy refers to the soft simmering reflection observed on the surface of the bead when light hits its surface. One can see beautiful silk like bands that move along the bead as it is moved in light. All tiger eye natural stone beads reflect this chatoyancy.

Because of the chatoyancy effect, the blue tiger stone is also referred to as the “Hawk’s Eye”. Blue tiger eye, however, is thought to be the most powerful of the tiger eye stones.

The fact that the blue tiger eye natural stone is also referred to as the “Hawk’s Eye” means that it is associated with focus and eyesight. In the literal sense, blue tiger eye stones are thought to help with poor eye sight and vision, enhancing the ability to focus on objects.', 'Capricorn', 'Throat'),
  ('BlueAragonite', 'Stone of soothing and calming emotional bodies', 'As well as sharing the same transformative and chakra balancing properties as normal Aragonite, Blue Aragonite helps one calm and soothe their emotional body. Simply holding a piece will imbue ones aura with a sense of relief and relaxation that can’t be put into words. One becomes more open with themselves and their “hidden” emotions, slowly overtime releasing these weights to the surface to be faced. Blue Aragonite is a very special stone that is here to soften emotional transitions. This could stem from traumatic events that we refuse to deal with, to mourning the loss of someone and not being able to cope with grief, as well as just having trouble getting over a recent falling out in a serious relationship. This stone will become your best friend in times of need as it will “soften” even the most hurtful emotions and events we relive day in and day out. Working with or carrying this stone daily will provide ones aura with powerful vibrations that can even be felt by the ones closest to us.', 'capricorn', 'third eye, throat, heart'),
  ('Boji Stone', 'Stone of  Uplifting  Channeling, Earth/Nature', 'Boji Stones Properties and Meaning – Boji Stones are composed of Pyrite, Palladium, Fossil and Petrified Bone. Boji Stones are found in only one spot, near a pyramid mound in Kansas USA.', 'Scorpio, Aquarius', 'All (when used in pairs)'),
  ('Boulder Opals', 'stone for Promotes harmony in friendships and partnerships', 'Boulder Opals are said to clear and cleanse one’s aura, wrap a protective shield around the wearer and allow the heart to become pure. Once the heart is pure, the body can receive the healing it requires. Another benefit from a pure heart is attracting or appreciating true love.', 'Libra and Scorpio.', 'Crown'),
  ('Brandberg Quartz', 'Stone for help in keeping cool and calm under great pressure', 'andenberg Quartz is a master healer, a rare and sacred crystal of high vibration that bridges realms and dimensions. It channels pure light for healing on every level—physical, emotional, mental, and spiritual—guiding the soul through deep transformation. This ethereal stone aligns the subtle bodies, dissolves energetic blockages, and awakens inner wisdom. Especially powerful for those lost in shadow—those feeling heavy, wounded, or trapped—it gently restores the spirit, rekindles hope, and opens the path to higher consciousness.', 'pisces, aquarius', 'crown and third eye'),
  ('Brazilian Amazonite', 'stone of peace', 'Amazonite has the healing powers to help with physical ailments as it releases emotional issues. Works as a catalyst in Energy Healing and chakra balancing. Amazonite crystal therapies are primarily associated with filtering out stresses, healing traumas, and soothing energies in the home and workplace. Use to facilitate speaking your truth with honour, integrity and trust. Helps balance male and female energies. Heals the after-effects of emotional trauma. Eases the transition into the afterlife making it more peaceful.', 'Virgo, Gemini', 'Throat'),
  ('Bronzite', 'stone of powerful healing energies', 'Brown/bronze in colour, Bronzite is used in healing for training oneself to listen to the rhythm and cycles of ones own natural state of being. If drawn to this stone, you are being shown very simply how to look after yourself.



Usually, it is trying to tell you to watch your diet and make changes because your diet may be too acidic or you may be consuming too many calories. You may need to think about the reason behind your poor choices regarding this.

Are you over compensating for something that is difficult for you or lacking in your life?

There is a time for action and a time to rest. This stone helps you to flow with your natural rhythm.  It is linked with the base chakra.', 'Leo', 'base'),
  ('Brookite', 'stone of awareness and communication', 'Brookite is a very high vibrational crystal that is believed to activate the upper chakras and facilitate work within them.


It is a wonderful aide if you are looking to develop your spiritual gifts and is said to support the ascension process by increasing ones own vibration and allowing us to see our status as light beings.

If you are looking to connect to the spiritual realms, Brookite will help to expand ones awareness and communication abilities. Use to connect to guides, angels or loved ones.

Whilst this is definitely a stone of the higher dimensions, it will also help to aid one in their acceptance of their own physicality.

The properties of Brookite will be naturally amplified within clear quartz and Brookite in Quartz will also hold the properties that Clear Quartz has to offer.', 'cancer', 'crown, third eye and soul star chakra'),
  ('Brucite', 'stone of confidence or struggling with a sense of self worth', 'Brucite is another new and rare mineral. It can come in the colour range red, yellow, green, blue,grey and white depending on the impurities in it. It is a magnesium hydroxide mineral that can be found in many parts of the world.


The canary yellow type is considered most rare as it comes from one location in Killarney, Saifullah District, Baluchistan, Pakistan.

Yellow Brucite doesn’t feel like other minerals, it feels unique. It has its own identity. Used on the solar plexus chakra to balance the energies there Brucite pushes the energy up to the heart to activate heart felt relationships to all things. Everything in right relationship to the self. A wonderful tool for those needing confidence or struggling with a sense of self worth. Balancing these two chakras, the solar plexus and the heart means the mind is clear to be decisive and chose directions that further one along their path of development.', 'Taurus', 'solar plexus'),
  ('Buddstone', 'stone for increases our senses', 'Buddstone increases our senses, particularly hearing and aligns our intuition at a ground level. Buddstone is a type of Jade from South Africa. A strengthening stone, it encourages self-sufficiency, realising potential and remaining true to finding our life purpose.', 'Taurus', 'Heart Chakra'),
  ('Calcite - Blue', 'stone for develop psychic gifts', 'Avalon Stone, found in Glastonbury, features earthy tones of black, brown, and occasional white. Formed over 195 million years ago, it’s made of limestone and mudstone. Energetically, Avalon Stone is highly protective, absorbing negativity and shielding against emotional stress—especially useful when traveling or navigating unfamiliar environments. Emotionally, it brings hidden fears, insecurities, and suppressed feelings to light, encouraging healing and release. As darkness transforms into light, the stone symbolizes renewal and new beginnings. Gentle yet powerful, Avalon Stone supports emotional clarity by helping you work through blockages one step at a time. Linked to Glastonbury, the heart chakra of the Earth, it invites you to embrace your full self and reconnect with inner peace and strength through conscious presence.', 'Cancer', 'third eye'),
  ('Calcite - Clear', 'stone for alleviates fear and stress', 'Its association with foreign atoms and minerals cause drastic colour variations and dilutions of character. It is often compared to the spiritual evolution of humankind as both go through many transformations along their journey. There are as many natural colours to calcite as there are chakras on the body, conveniently one to balance every energy centre.

Calcite works by your intuition. The colour you are drawn to would be the right one for you to start with. Once the body has dealt with this, you will automatically be drawn to another one. Gradually you will find, that just like the Calcite changed and evolved, so will you. This is by learning to trust in your body and your mind’s own abilities.

Calcite alleviates fear and stress. It is considered to be a balancer of the male and female energies. It helps us to gain our composure and gives us control over our emotions. It can encourage us to simply ‘be’ in order to receive inspiration and guidance. It assists in decision-making and clarifies dreams, visions and channelling.', 'Cancer, Leo and Aquarius', 'ALL'),
  ('Calcite - Green', 'stone of strong emotions', 'Green Calcite is often used on the body just below the heart chakra and works on the adrenal glands, the nervous system, the digestion and all bacterial growth infections. It is also renowned for its success in dealing with mental fears, soothing anxieties and grounding chaotic energies.


In the aura Green Calcite cleanses like a spring clean. It has the potential to refresh the many layers of the aura like a reset button bringing it back into the intentional state of wholeness. This, of course may take some time depending on how much baggage one has accumulated there and on how willing one is to let it go. However any putting down or dissolving of useless baggage is a benefit and will ultimately lead to a better state of being. xieties and grounding chaotic energies.', 'Cancer', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Amber Calcite - Honey Calcite', 'stone of confidence, motivation and determination', 'Amber Calcite, also known as Honey Calcite, is a crystalline form of calcium carbonate, originating from marine organisms and evolving over time into limestone, then marble. Found worldwide, it can be translucent or fluorescent, and its many colour variations mirror the transformations of the human spirit. Each hue corresponds with a chakra, making Calcite a versatile energy balancer.

Intuitively guided, you’ll be drawn to the colour your body needs most. As you heal and grow, your preferences will shift. Honey Calcite, in particular, supports emotional balance, eases fear and stress, and encourages clarity and decision-making. It uplifts the aura, works with the solar plexus, crown, and root chakras, and aids spiritual development.', 'Cancer', 'Base, solar plexus, third eye'),
  ('Calcite - Lemurian Aquatine', 'stone of calm and brings into the sought after lucid awareness.', 'Lemurian Aquatine Calcite is a gentle crystal ranging from pale to deep blue-green, known for its soft, soothing energy. It supports access to the theta state—a dreamy, meditative space between waking and sleep—ideal for lucid dreaming, hypnosis, and astral travel. This stone is often used to connect with Lemurian wisdom and ancient knowledge. It guides those experiencing spiritual awakening, helping them trust that they are already spiritually aware. Holding this stone can bring comfort and insight during times of inner exploration. When gently stroked around the body, it has a calming, cooling effect on the emotional field, like a lullaby for the soul. Would you like this version formatted for a product listing or educational display?', 'Cancer', 'the heart, throat, third eye and crown chakra'),
  ('Calcite - Mango', 'stone of love and stress reliever', 'Manganocalcite, commonly known as Mango Calcite, is a gentle yet powerful crystal believed to support connection with angelic realms and offer glimpses beyond the veil. It carries a nurturing love energy that encourages self-care without guilt, teaching that we can only give our best when we feel our best. Mango Calcite soothes frustration and promotes kindness, love, and respect, making it especially helpful for children aged 4–7. During this key developmental stage, it helps them navigate growing independence, emotional expression, and boundary testing. For parents, Mango Calcite offers a calming bridge of connection as children grow. Holding or playing with the crystal can steady emotions, support thoughtful communication, and offer a sense of comfort. It is said to draw angels near, offering reassurance and peace—even when one doesn’t know they need it. Mango Calcite is a compassionate guide during emotional transitions for both children and adults.', 'Taurus, Libra, Cancer', 'Heart Chakra'),
  ('Calcite - Orange', 'stone of Creativity, sexuality,confidence, innovation', 'Manganocalcite, commonly known as Mango Calcite, is a gentle yet powerful crystal believed to support connection with angelic realms and offer glimpses beyond the veil. It carries a nurturing love energy that encourages self-care without guilt, teaching that we can only give our best when we feel our best. Mango Calcite soothes frustration and promotes kindness, love, and respect, making it especially helpful for children aged 4–7. During this key developmental stage, it helps them navigate growing independence, emotional expression, and boundary testing. For parents, Mango Calcite offers a calming bridge of connection as children grow. Holding or playing with the crystal can steady emotions, support thoughtful communication, and offer a sense of comfort. It is said to draw angels near, offering reassurance and peace—even when one doesn’t know they need it. Mango Calcite is a compassionate guide during emotional transitions for both children and adults.', 'Cancer, Leo.', 'Sacral, solar plexus'),
  ('Calcite - Pink Cobaltian 
***correction to name - Cobaltian Calcite', 'stone of positiveness', 'Who could not feel joy holding and admiring this little beauty.  From the name you will have guessed that it gets its amazing colour from the presence of Cobalt and the small amount we ever get in is from Morocco, Africa.


Colbaltian Calcite works beautifully on the heart chakra unburdening emotions of loss, grief and long buried hurts and regrets. By working with this mineral you will find that it stimulates the higher chakras into alignment allowing logic and reason to gradually seep into your psyche bringing acceptance and courage.', 'Cancer, Capricorn', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Calcite - Red', 'stone  of  encourage emotional strength', 'Red Calcite works on the base chakra – dealing with vitality and the physical will to survive. Healers believe it relieves constipation, acts on pain and stress relating to the lower spinal column and on the support of bone density.


Red Calcite is a hard worker; it tackles many physical problems of the skeletal structure. It also encourages emotional strength.', 'Cancer', 'Root Chakra'),
  ('Carnelian', 'Stone of courage passion and power', 'Carnelian gives off a bold, warm energy that stimulates the first three chakras. Its vibrations draw in massive amounts of life force, sexual and creative energies, and assertive will. It aids in building confidence, courage, passion and power, making it a great stone for those who are shy or passive in life. It is a very powerful stone that can be of great assistance when one needs to take action, aiding one in conquering procrastination, as well as jumping from old ways and dedicating themselves to a new path. This stone is extremely helpful for those who purely wish for good things but have difficulty making them happen, and for those who tend to focus primarily on spiritual work (working primarily with the 4th-7th chakras) and neglect the the physical aspects of life (that deal with the 1st-3rd chakras). Misbalance of this sort can lead to ineffectiveness in one’s endeavors and loss of power over one’s life. Carnelian also encourages one to stop waiting for their dreams to come true and to make them happen through channels of Divine Will. This special stone helps one to take more risks that often come with taking strong, assertive action.', 'Taurus, cancer, leo, virgo', 'Root, sacral, solar plexus'),
  ('Carnelian Lace Bracelet', 'stone fors timulates the metabolism.', 'This beautiful Bracelet is made of 6mm Carnelian Lace Beads. Carnelian is a stabilizing crystal with a high energy vibration. An excellent crystal to restore vitality and motivation. Carnelian never needs cleansing, furthermore, it will keep other crystals cleansed. Encourages and promotes positive life choices. Helps you trust yourself. Stimulates the metabolism.

Activates the sacral chakra and influence reproductive system, increases fertility. Carnelian improves the absorption of vitamins and minerals, ensure good supply of blood to organs and tissues. For someone going through the dying transition, Carnelian helps remove fear of death.

Carnelian is better known for its effects on the Sacral chakra, but it is an excellent crystal for the Third Eye and helps with insight and clairvoyance. Carry Carnelian when needed to increase "joie de vivre" and stamina. Meditate with Carnelian to help with transitions or increase insight.', 'Taurus, Cancer, Leo, Scorpio', 'Sacral, Third Eye'),
  ('Cascading Quartz', 'full of ancient wisdom and knowledge', 'Cascading Quartz Crystals is also known as Candlestick Quartz and Pineapple Quartz. They are crystals that have an appearance of many triangular crystal forms running down the side of the crystal!', '', ''),
  ('Cassiterite', 'stone for strong grounding energy', 'Cassiterite, also known as tinstone, is a grounding mineral often found within Quartz and colored by hematite, giving it warm yellow to orange hues. It’s especially helpful for those who feel disconnected from their body, family, or place in the world—offering a sense of belonging and grounding. This can be particularly powerful for individuals with complex origins, such as IVF births, who may feel spiritually misplaced. Cassiterite helps anchor the physical body and encourages acceptance of one’s life journey. It’s also supportive in processing feelings of rejection and emotional disconnection. Used during meditation or dream work, it may assist in reaching the deep, peaceful theta state for profound healing.', 'Sagittarius', 'root chakra'),
  ('Cat’s Eye', 'stone of forgiveness, peace of mind, determination, strength of mind, steadfastness', 'Cat’s Eye is a stone of new beginnings, releases old patterns which no longer serve you and inspires self confidence. It derived its name form the fibrous inclusions that give it a shining quality like a cat’s eye. Used for thousands of years as a good luck charm, believed to bring luck and ward away the evil eye. It has also been used to protect against spells, curses and death. Cat’s Eye makes a very effective protective talisman.  

Fosters intellect, wisdom and gives a better understanding of how to solve problems. Increases personnel power and deepens spirituality. Promotes forgiveness, peace of mind, determination, strength of mind, steadfastness, willpower, moral, courage, vigour, self control, good luck, intelligence and knowledge. Some of its many benefits include stabilizing emotions and balancing the metabolism. Carry Cat’s Eye with you or place in your pillowcase to benefit from its vibrations.', 'Capricorn, Aries, Taurus', 'Solar Plexus, Crown'),
  ('Cathedral Quartz', 'stone for  enhances spiritual growth, spirituality and wisdom', 'Cathedral Quartz forms in the shape of castle/cathedrals. They come in Smoky, Clear and Citrine Quartz Flavors. In the 90’s a Brazilian family started calling Amethyst geodes Cathedrals.', 'All', 'Third Eye, Crown, Etheric and Transpersonal'),
  ('Cavansite', 'Stone of intuition', 'Cavansite is a stone of transition through major life changes. It aids you to let go of faulty thinking and be comfortable in the knowledge of your actions. , focusing second sight and activating channeling abilities with Blue Ray energetic vibrations.', 'aquarius', 'Throat'),
  ('Celestine', 'stone of wisdom, understanding, mindfulness and higher consciousness', 'This pale blue crystal has a beautiful gentle and calming energy. It is used by healers for soothing fretful children and makes a wonderful addition to a child’s bedroom. Celestine instils peace.

Read More

Known as the ‘teacher’, this crystal is widely believed to have the ability to ‘jump-start’ awareness of the higher self. It is used by those starting our on their path of self-discovery, or by those who may have become lost, to recover higher consciousness. It is the crystal to work with for contacting your guardian angels or for creating a clear channel when opening up to explore the celestial realms.  Celestine promotes awareness and sensitivity of the etheric self by identifying troubled parts of the aura and restoring balance. Celestine reveals truths, It shows what is hidden and aids acceptance.', 'Aries', 'third eye'),
  ('Celestite', 'Stone of Divine Vibrations', 'The high vibrations of Celestite crystal healing properties stimulate and support the throat, third eye, and crown chakras, making it an excellent stone for an overall spiritual detox. In meditation, Celestite helps ease the transition into a peaceful state of awareness, which can be challenging for a troubled mind amped up with conflict and frustration.', 'Libra, Gemini', 'throat'),
  ('Chalcedony', 'stone for eliminate depression, fear and hysteria', 'Purple chalcedony mainly presents themselves as reddish purple and dark purple. Among them, deep reddish purple chalcedony with no impurities are top grade. The crystal of the stone is opaque to translucent, with a hardness of 6-8 and a specific gravity of 2.581.

Chalcedony colors vary depending on its components, categories including purple chalcedony, onyx, light chalcedony, red chalcedony, and green chalcedony, etc. All are very popular!', 'Gemini', 'throat'),
  ('Chalcedony - Blue', 'stone for self-love, mothering and healing the inner child', 'Blue Chalcedony is a member of the Quartz family and unusually by nature has a translucent or opaque, waxy, dull appearance. It is particularly beautiful and many are attracted to it for its gentle energy.



Some pieces contain a small amount of Opal and in fact are often mistaken for low grade Opal. It is the nurturing crystal for self-love, mothering and healing the inner child. Hold the crystal close to the heart and affirm the intention to love thyself and others as equals.

Chalcedony can aid the memory and works well with global transient amnesia. It allows peace to enter the soul and balances the higher and lower chakras.', 'Gemini.', 'Throat'),
  ('Chalcedony - Copper', 'stone for stimulates independence and action', 'Copper Chalcedony has the same properties as the Blue Chalcedony and is also able to help combat lethargy. It has a stronger quality to it that stimulates independence and action. It is strong willed and defiant, not wishing to share space with other crystals easily. However with some people, it will tolerate and work in conjunction with Carnelian on lethargy.


It works in the circulatory system aiding blood flow, cleaning, clearing and restoring optimum health.', 'Cancer, Virgo, Sagittarius, and Aquarius', 'Throat'),
  ('Chalcopyrite', 'Stone of Luck and Good Fortune & New Beginnings', 'Chalcopyrite is a powerful stone that activates and aligns all chakras. It''s a powerful tool that has been used to remove blockages of chakras by shamans and reiki professionals. This stone offers up transformative energies that assist in changing of habits, routines and lifestyles. Working with this stone will help one in finding their own way and life meaning. Carrying this stone daily is ideal for anyone feeling like their “stuck” in the same daily motions and are looking for a sudden change. This stone has always been associated with opportunity and new beginnings, and has been commonly used as a trinket for obtaining luck. Although this stone actives all chakras, it specifically resonates with the higher 3 chakras. Chalcopyrite has been known to expand the mind and open it up to a higher realm. This stone opens our third eye to endless visions when meditating with it, while also using our crown chakra to bridge the gap between physical and spiritual realms. The energies of this stone on the throat chakra specifically help in bringing in this knowledge to the physical. By being able to talk about what you see, feel and hear, you are making it a physical emotion, confirming its reality. That energy can manifest and bring with it positive and life changing opportunities.', 'Capricorn', 'all'),
  ('Channel Quartz', 'stone for communicate with your subconscious self', 'Channel quartz Crystals have a large seven sided face on the front of the termination and a three sided face on the back. Usually they form on Clear Quartz Crystals, but can also appear on Smoky and Amethyst Quartz Crystals.', '', ''),
  ('Charoite', 'Stone of bridging the higher dimensions with the physical plane', 'Charoite is a powerful stone of transformation that bridges the heart and crown chakras, aligning spiritual insight with unconditional love. It helps release unconscious fears and supports the transmutation of old emotional patterns, encouraging acceptance of the present moment. Charoite inspires service to others and the world, activating inner wisdom and compassion. It assists in overcoming compulsions and embracing change with grace. This stone promotes unity, helping one accept others without judgment and build stronger relationships. With its grounding presence, Charoite clears mental clutter, enhances synchronicity, and supports the realization that every moment is part of a perfect, unfolding path toward one''s highest self.', 'virgo, scorpio, sagittarius', 'etheric, crown, third eye, heart, solar plexus, earthstar'),
  ('Charoite in Tinaksite', 'stone of positive thinking and inspiration', '(The name Tinaksite is derived from its composition: titanium (Ti), sodium (Na) potassium (K) and silicon (Si).)



Tinaksite works well with Charoite as it helps to defragment the mind from mental stress and chatter. Calms the noise of the inner voice. The doubts and fears that are tumbled around and haunt every waking moment. It’s a bringer of peace and serenity. Of visions, dreams and shadow-walking. For travelling to the Hall of Learning and bringing back wisdom and for astral travel.

See also Charoite', '', 'solar plexus and crown chakras'),
  ('Chevron Amethyst', 'stone  of  peace and serenity', 'Charoite is a powerful stone of transformation that bridges the heart and crown chakras, aligning spiritual insight with unconditional love. It helps release unconscious fears and supports the transmutation of old emotional patterns, encouraging acceptance of the present moment. Charoite inspires service to others and the world, activating inner wisdom and compassion. It assists in overcoming compulsions and embracing change with grace. This stone promotes unity, helping one accept others without judgment and build stronger relationships. With its grounding presence, Charoite clears mental clutter, enhances synchronicity, and supports the realization that every moment is part of a perfect, unfolding path toward one''s highest self.', 'Aquarius, Pisces, Gemini', 'Crown, Third Eye'),
  ('Chevron Prasiolite', 'stone for protect and repel low vibrating energies', 'Also called Green Amethyst, most Prasiolite stones are produced by heat treatment. Natural amethyst is heated, in a laboratory until the colour changes from purple to yellow-green or green. The Amethyst used to produce Prasiolite usually comes from the USA, or Brazil. 

Natural Prasiolite is a relatively rare gemstone, that came from Brazil. However, it is now also sourced in USA, Poland and in Thunder Bay, Canada. Like Amethyst, Prasiolite is best kept out of direct sunlight, as it will fade to almost clear colour. 

Chevron Prasiolite displays chevrons, v-shapes, of Snowy Quartz beautifully layered between the greens. A Third Eye and Crown gemstone, Prasiolite assists in opening up spiritually and developing psychic abilities. Chevron Prasiolite, like Chevron Amethyst, has a very strong, focused energy that protects from negative energies and is an excellent healer, both physically and spiritually. 

Used during out of body travel or shamanic journeys, it will protect and repel low vibrating energies. A beautiful gemstone for meditating, Chevron Prasiolite can balance all of the Chakras.', 'Capricorn, Scorpio', 'Third Eye, Crown, Heart'),
  ('Chiastolite', 'stone of  protection from evil', 'Chiastolite crystal is also known as Cross Stone. Ancient people used it as a Cross because of the cross sign on this crystal. Using the sign of the cross is based on prehistoric times. In different cultures in all known times, the cross has been used in symbolic meanings. It is accepted that the t-columns in Gobeklitepe, which is accepted as the oldest place of worship, symbolize the human body. It has always been the sign of the cross among the most significant symbols of these places that people gather to protection, and use to glorify their creators. The common point of these uses is to prevent, stop, or reverse something. So it is protection from evil.', 'Libra', 'crown'),
  ('Chlorite Included Quartz', 'stone for physical regeneration, especially as an elixir', 'Chlorite Included Quartz Crystals have the mineral Chlorite inside and sometimes on the outside of them. On occasions the Chlorite can appear in the shape of a Phantom Quartz.', '', ''),
  ('Chrome Diopside', 'Stone of powerful healing, knowledge and transformation', 'Chrome Diopside is a rare and powerful stone, revered for its deep healing and spiritual insights. It channels pure restorative energy, helping to uncover past life experiences and emotional scars embedded within the soul. Diopside resonates deeply, reaching beyond the limits of the mind to bring understanding to past trauma and unresolved emotions. Through meditation, it opens pathways to healing by releasing subconscious protective barriers around the heart. As one aligns with its energy, Diopside facilitates visionary experiences and enhances connection to past wisdom. This mineral supports personal transformation, helping you integrate lessons from previous lifetimes for profound spiritual growth.', 'libra and virgo', 'Heart and root'),
  ('Chrysanthemum Stone', 'Stone to activate inherent gifts', 'Chrysanthemum Stone is a stone of harmony, emitting a calm, confident energy that encourages one to slow down, center, and enjoy the moment, lending the time needed for one to “bloom.”', 'Taurus', 'earth star'),
  ('Chrysocolla', 'A stone of empowerment, communication , and calming', 'Chrysocolla is a stone of empowerment, communication , and calming. People who tend to get erratic and are hyper emotional during stressful situations need to carry a piece of Chrysocolla daily. This stone will help in reducing that panic feeling when overwhelmed, and will allow you to have a clear head and a calm mind while making difficult decisions. Chrysocolla will aid in communicating those thoughts while raising your wisdom to achieve these ideas in reality. Chrysocolla is commonly worn around the neck near the throat chakra for the maximum effects of its abilities.', 'Taurus, Gemini, Virgo', 'Throat, heart, root'),
  ('Chrysoprase (Australian Jade)', 'Stone to activate the heart chakra', 'Chrysoprase is a stone of the heart that is here to fill ones aura with strong healing energies. This stone will help activate and open one''s heart chakra, making it easier to get in touch with your emotional body. By being better in touch with yourself, one will soon realize the inner strength in which they posses. Chrysoprase urges us to channel the newly found strength directly into our heart space, attempting to cleanse and rid all negative energy. This special crystal also helps one activate and unlock their solar plexus chakra. This chakra is the source of our personal will, and with that anything can become possible. Our personal will is the driving force behind all that we do out of love. This unquenchable desire pushes us into action while providing laser sharp focus, increased stamina, strength, determination, and awareness. What makes Chrysoprase such a powerful stone is the ability to provide a connection between our solar plexus chakra and our heart space. With this connection, we are able to easily access and use the above traits with intentions that come from the heart, not just our will. This will provide one the strength to truly focus on doing what their heart desires. Making ones heart feel complete is the true meaning of happiness and serenity, and Chrysoprase is a power crystal that will help get you there.', 'Libra', 'heart, solar plexus'),
  ('Chrysotile serpentine', 'stone of life and holds the energies', 'Serpentine is a group of green stones found globally, from Canada to Greece, Korea, and New Zealand. While often confused with jade, its chemical composition is distinct. The serpentine group includes around twenty related minerals, formed in two primary types: antigorite and chrysotile. Antigorite is solid, while chrysotile is fibrous and a form of asbestos, a dangerous mineral known to cause severe respiratory issues. Chrysotile should be avoided for metaphysical purposes. Antigorite, in contrast, is softer and has a shiny green appearance due to chromium and cobalt minerals. Serpentine stones vary from translucent to opaque, with translucent stones typically enhancing psychic abilities, while opaque ones influence the material world more.', 'GEMINI', 'heart'),
  ('Cinnabar', 'Stone of transformation', 'Cinnabar is a transformation stone that can push one on an internal expedition of truth, change, and self discovery. It’s potent energies engage our root and sacral chakras, connecting the two and enhancing their external benefits. The attachment to the useless materials around us will cease to exist. All of your remaining life force energy will be turned directly in line with one''s true higher self. The path in which you set out on will only become more easily understood as you meditate and tap into Cinnabar’s energy. One will become more in touch with their spiritual body. This will allow our spiritual body to make decisions rather than our clouded minds that are so easily distracted. Another great quality of Cinnabar that one can benefit from is the ability to take control of their actions. This slight change can benefit all aspects of your life, and drastically change the path you take. One’s ability to control themselves, through willpower and determination, will lead them to one of the most powerful abilities of the human mind; manifesting your destiny. This is something no other being on this planet can do, except for you. You are the only true visionary for yourself as no other soul can see, feel or embody the real you. Let Cinnabar’s energy show you the power you have within, through deep meditative sessions that bring to life the “real” you.', 'Leo', 'Sacral, Root'),
  ('Cinnabar in Quartz', 'stone for attract wealth', 'Cinnabar is linked to the High Priestess card in the Tarot, embodying temptation, mystery, and power. It is a teacher of life’s deeper truths. The message it brings is that while you may learn, plan, and hope, some things are simply not meant to be. Some desires, like forbidden love or a child not for this lifetime, are not for you. Cinnabar’s lesson is acceptance of this truth. This magical crystal brings focus, clarity, and spiritual mastery, refining energies within the body and chakras. Meditation with Cinnabar can signal great change. Be cautious, as Cinnabar may contain mercury in its rough form.', 'Leo', 'sacral, third eye, and root chakras'),
  ('Citrine', 'Stone of Small Fortune', 'Citrine is a beautiful yellow-orange stone and is known for attracting wealth and abundance. ... If you are looking to bring more money into your life, using a citrine can be an easy way to help align yourself with wealth and abundance!', 'Sagittarius', 'Sacral'),
  ('Clear Quartz', 'Stone of Clarification', 'Clear Quartz enhances psychic abilities. It aids concentration and unlocks memory. Stimulates the immune system and brings the body into balance. Clear Quartz (Crystal Quartz, Rock Crystal) harmonises all the chakras and aligns the subtle bodies', 'All', 'Crown'),
  ('Colombian Quartz', 'stone for cleansing toxicity from the body, mind and spirit', 'Colombian Quartz Crystals are gathered from the Emerald mining area of Colombia. These crystals are exceptionally bright and clear, many have striations with Lemurian Form! Read more about Colombian Quartz healing properties', 'Capricorn', 'Crown, Upper Crown'),
  ('Connemara Marble', 'stone for strength of character', 'Metamorphosed limestone, forms in course to med grained rock typically of dolomites and calcites. Connemara Marble is green in colour and our supply comes from Ireland. A powerful serenity stone helps master thought control and instil peace.



Many believe this a lucky stone and that it brings the holder of the stone contact with the elementals. The gift of seeing and conversing with faerie folk and an understanding of the animal and plant kingdoms. Connemara Marble builds strength of character and is often given as gift to new born babies.

Stamina endurance and determination are qualities of this stone.', 'na', 'heart'),
  ('Red coral', 'stone of protective healing energies for women and children', 'Red coral works on the base chakra and has a connection to the earth, peace for humanity and harmony for all kingdoms. It vibrates at a lower frequency. It is a wonderful healer and teacher.', 'Aries', 'Root'),
  ('Coral Fossil', 'stone for helpful for the absorption of nutrients', 'Coral Fossil has been used by sailors for eons as a good luck charm to protect against storms. It is said to promote longevity. Fossil Coral aligns all the Chakras and it stimulates clairaudience abilities. 

In life, this fossil also protects against emotional storms. It has a calming effect that eases the emotional temperament possessed by some. Coral Fossil creates a peaceful aura and thus inner peace. This gemstone is very helpful for the absorption of nutrients, the healing of the stomach and intestines.', 'Pisces', 'All'),
  ('Crackled Quartz', 'stone of Self-discipline', 'Crackled Quartz is a powerful healing stone known for its striking appearance and energetic properties. Formed when Quartz is heated and then rapidly cooled, creating a crackled effect, it carries the energy of transformation and renewal. This stone is believed to amplify energy and promote emotional healing by breaking down old patterns, allowing for personal growth. It encourages clarity of thought, enhances creativity, and provides a strong protective shield against negativity. Crackled Quartz is also thought to help release stress and promote a sense of inner peace, supporting one’s journey towards balance and self-awareness.', 'All', 'Depends on colour'),
  ('Creedite', 'Stone to tune into higher realms', 'Creedite is a high-energy stone known for its ability to attune one to higher spiritual vibrations. It uplifts vibrations, allowing for experiences in higher realms, channeling messages, and connecting with universal wisdom. Creedite enhances spiritual communication, assisting in attunement with the Akashic Records and interpreting messages from spirit guides. It helps understand abstract communications from higher realms, making it an excellent ally for those seeking deeper spiritual insights. This stone is especially effective for those beginning new spiritual journeys or unfamiliar with crystals, as it expands sensitivity to energy and overall awareness. Creedite provides clarity, helping one reach higher frequencies and understanding.', 'Virgo', 'Etheric, crown, third eye, throat'),
  ('Crocoite', 'Stone for grounding', 'Crocoite is a very interesting mineral that gives off a high vibrational energy. This mineral works to activate, unlock and link your root, heart, and crown chakras together. This important connection helps you root your most important thoughts and emotions down to an earthly plane so that they can then be grounded. Only once you are able to come to terms with your ideas and emotions, can you move forward and take action. The most important step when trying to do this is just taking the initial jump. A lot of people have trouble making the leap due to fear and insecurities, but Crocoite can be the perfect ally. This special mineral helps keep your mind focused and clear when on the path of following your dreams. It provides you with “tunnel vision” to help avoid distractions and derailments from your truest desires. Crocoite also assists you with keeping an open and clear heart space, allowing your truest emotions to channel through you. Being able to use your positive emotions while chasing after your goals will only enhance the experience thus making each and every moment meaningful.', 'Aries', 'Crown, heart, root'),
  ('Cross Crystal', 'stone of  making decisions', 'Cross Crystal are crystals that have another crystal lying across it. The second crystal may be at an angle like an X, or straight across in a traditional “Cross” shape.', 'na', 'crown'),
  ('Crystallized Rose Quartz', 'stone of bring beautiful loving change to ones life', 'Crystallized Rose Quartz comes from a small island in a large river running through Tacquaral, Minas Gerais, Brazil.', 'pisces, taurus, libra', 'Heart'),
  ('Cuprite', 'stone of strength, vitality, encouragement and support', 'Cuprite Crystal Healing Properties: Cuprite can activate, strengthen, and heal the base chakra, awakening kundalini and raising energy and vitality. It encourages connection with and balancing of the energy of the feminine archetype.

It resonates with the base chakra and carries a very grounding Earth Mother energy. It is the mineral of fertility, menstrual problems, emotional pain and fear of rejection, trauma, sexual trauma, circulation, metabolic imbalances and soothes hypertension. Holding Cuprite is extremely grounding for stress and worries over outside influences that one has no control over. It is a wonderful ally when working with rites of passage for the male or female energies. It helps heal a broken heart, alleviates guilt and a great mineral for those on a journey of self discovery.

Cuprite is a grand campaigner for the Goddess, for women and women’s mysteries.', 'aquarius', 'base chakra'),
  ('Dalmatian Jasper', 'Stone for grounding', 'Dalmatian Jasper is a stone that aids you to break down barriers that you have created as protection around yourself. It may also relieve the need to take revenge on anyone who you feel has done you wrong, as its vibration helps you to release any lack of trust in other people. This allows you to move forward in life and discover your true purpose for being here. Its energy brings childlike joy and a sense of playfulness into your life. The black spots are Black Tourmaline, and so it also embodies the energy of this stone, and will aid you with spiritual grounding and psychic protection. This stone has a lovely energy that reminds you that you can enjoy life, that its okay to have fun. The black spots of Tourmaline within it bring through an energy that encourages positive attitudes, good luck and happiness, irrespective of the conditions of your life.', 'all', 'root, sacral'),
  ('Danburite', 'stone of Soothing, Love, Stress Reduction, Empathy', 'Danburite Crystal Properties: Danburite is a member of the Sorosilicates family, forming in colors such as clear, white, pink, brown and yellow.', 'Leo', 'Heart, Crown'),
  ('Desert Rose Stone', 'stone for relieve stress and enhance will power', 'Desert Rose Selenite, also known as Gypsum Rose or Sand Rose, is a type of Selenite found in most deserts around the world. They range in sizes from pea-sized to many feet in length and width. 
Desert Rose is a stone of the mind. It promotes intuitive perception, mental ability and clarity. It calms the worries of the mind from distractions and disruptions. It clarifies thinking and perception. Desert Rose can be used to relieve stress and enhance will power. It is best to place at the bedside, near a favourite chair, in the home or office as it helps cleanse the auric field and the environment. As with Selenite, Desert Rose will clear and charge other gemstones it is placed near. Although they do not make good palm stones, because of their fragile states, adding them near a meditation chair, yoga mat or under a Reiki table will assist in removing blockages between Chakras and assist with the Chi energy flow.

A wonderful gemstone to manifest your dreams into reality, use in crystal grids as they will also cleanse and recharge the stones around them or hold gently while verbally stating your intentions.', 'Capricorn, Scorpio, Taurus, Aquarius', 'Root, Sacral, Crown'),
  ('Diamond', 'stone for promoting incredible power, emotional growth and loving energy.', 'Diamonds are a symbol of purity, strength, and eternal love. Known for their unmatched hardness and brilliance, they are often seen as a representation of clarity and illumination. Spiritually, diamonds are believed to bring light into the soul, helping to clear negative energies and bring emotional balance. They enhance mental clarity and are thought to strengthen the connection to higher consciousness, making them a powerful tool for meditation and spiritual work. Additionally, diamonds are said to inspire love, devotion, and commitment, making them an ideal stone for relationships, personal growth, and enhancing one''s connection to divine energy.', 'Aries', 'Crown'),
  ('Diopside', 'STone of new beginnings, opportunities, living in the moment', 'Diopside is a magnesium calcium silicate mineral that forms grainy masses and small prismatic shards. A member of the Pyroxene group, Diopside is known for its healing and restorative energy, offering pure vitality for each lifetime endured. Its vibrations resonate deeply within the soul, tapping into past life experiences and emotional scars. These scars are internalized, becoming part of one''s spiritual foundation. Meditating with Diopside, particularly over the heart, helps release emotional blockages and can lead to visionary experiences. This stone also aids in connecting with higher consciousness and understanding the deeper meanings behind dreams and past experiences.', 'libra and virgo', 'Heart and root'),
  ('Dioptase', 'Stone of forgiveness and letting go of past wrongs', 'Dioptase is a rare, vibrant green copper silicate mineral known for its intense color and powerful healing properties. It is often associated with emotional healing, particularly in addressing issues related to heartache and trauma. Dioptase is believed to help release old emotional wounds, bringing about a deep sense of inner peace and renewal. It is a stone of transformation, promoting healing of the heart and encouraging forgiveness, compassion, and emotional balance. Dioptase is also thought to stimulate personal growth and spiritual awakening, enhancing one’s ability to connect with higher consciousness and universal love. Its energy is both soothing and revitalizing.', 'Scorpio, Sagittarius', 'Heart'),
  ('Dolomite', 'stone for  release insomnia, nightmares, irregular sleep patterns.', 'The ‘giving’ stone, Dolomite is believed to encourage charitable actions and foster the selfless consciousness required for healing. It encourages impulsive, original thinking and is widely used as an aid to energy realignment.


It is used by healers to strengthen bones, teeth and the physical structure – bringing weaker parts of the body into line with the whole.', 'Aries, Taurus, Libra, Scorpio,', 'Third Eye chakra'),
  ('Doorway Quartz', 'stone for  spiritual growth, spirituality, awareness, and wisdom', 'Doorway Quartz have deeply recessed triangular “doorways” set into one or more of their termination faces. These doorway triangles may appear in most of the different types of quartz crystals available.', 'All esp Leo', 'crown chakra'),
  ('Double Terminated Quartz', '', 'Double Terminated Quartz crystals have a termination (point) at both ends of the crystal. They come in many shapes, sizes, and colors.', 'pisces', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Dragon’s Blood', 'stone of abundance and courage', 'Dragon’s Blood is only found in Australia, local legend says that the stone is the remains of deceased ancient dragons, the green being the skin and the red being the blood. Dragon’s Blood is a stone of abundance and courage, draws money and love to the wearer. An intensely healing stone, brings balance and enhances life force energy (Chi). Brings more energy into the auric field and the physical body.  

Helpful when you want to change your persona as it invests in you with dignity and powers to make you stronger, helping you achieve goals. Emotionally, helps develop self-confidence, a strong will and love. It calls forth the gentle strengths of love, forgiveness, and compassion; thous taming the inner dragon. Dragon’s Blood helps release energy blockages, great for Yin Yang balance, the Aura, and heals the physical heart. Full of Prana energy, Dragon’s Blood helps to reset the body into an energy of health. As its name suggests, a go-to crystal for blood purification. It is an excellent stone for bronchitis, backache, colds and flu, jaundice, and Multiple Sclerosis (MS). 

Dragon’s Blood is strongly energetic when placed into wallet or cash box to increase income and hold on to wealth. Grid with this stone to increase wealth and financial stability. Wear Dragon’s blood to help manifest good luck and to keep you healthy, centered and grounded.', 'Leo', 'Root, Sacral, Heart'),
  ('Dumortierite', 'stone for patience', 'Dumortierite is referred to as the stone for patience. It is a great crystal to help with memory and confidence. Beneficial for students who want to increase their will power and motivation to learn.  An excellent crystal for those who want to develop their gift of clairvoyance. 

Place a tumbled piece of Dumortierite behind the ear to open clairaudience (psychic hearing), place in front of the ear to stimulate past-life memories.  Place just above the Third Eye Chakra on the forehead, to break ties, form contracts and agreements made over time, that no longer serve you. Beneficial in releasing past life dis-ease, or relationships in present life. Makes a great grid to help with memory.', 'Leo, Aquarius', 'Throat, Third Eye'),
  ('Durangite', 'stone of Expressive Ability, Anti-Stress/Anxiety', 'Durangite is a member of the Arsenate family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from orange to red. This mineral is quite rare.', 'Virgo', 'All, Extra Focus on Throat'),
  ('Elestial Quartz', 'stone of power and  effective elixirs', 'Elestials are known by many names, such as Crocodile Quartz, Jacare Quartz and Skeletal Quartz. They form in Smoky Quartz, Citrine Quartz, Amethyst, and rare cases, Rose Quartz flavors.', 'Capricorn, Sagittarius, Scorpio', 'All'),
  ('Emerald', 'stone of successful love', 'Emeralds, often referred to as the "Stone of Love," are known for bringing emotional and rational balance to relationships. They are deeply connected to the heart chakra, making them excellent for healing and promoting love, truth, and honesty. Emeralds are commonly used in engagement rings, symbolizing unconditional love, harmony, and balance. Historically, they were worn by high priests in ancient Egypt, where they were believed to have healing properties, often crushed into powders for medicinal use.

Emeralds also support physical healing, especially for colds, flu, and breathing difficulties. By placing a tumbled emerald over the heart and Baltic amber near the throat chakra, they can stimulate healing and energy balance. These stones are also helpful in clearing mental fog, improving memory, and enhancing emotional stability.

Emeralds are ideal for spiritual work, particularly in Theta healing, promoting focus, calm, and healing of physical ailments like muscle atrophy or fibromyalgia, encouraging recovery and motivation.', 'taurus', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Empowerite', 'stone of courage and strength', 'Empowerite has come to our attention and recently become available from New Zealand as a new on the scene mineral that is considered rare. Being new to us we have little information on its potential healing qualities. So we will give the information we have and update it as we hear back from healers and our customers.



We do know that is is very collectible and sought after and there is not much about at the moment. Found under masses of deep organic vegetation in the forests of New Zealand Empowerite is a variety of Chert.

Cryptoctystalline or polycrystalline Quartz will normally form as nodules in Limestone and this is generally how Chert forms. Some say that Empowerite is simply Flint with a fancy name however although flint is a variety of Chert, flint is a material that forms in chalk or marlstone.

Empowerite doesn’t feel anything like flint and the pieces coming on the market don’t even look like flint. They do feel interesting though. There is a subtle buzz one feels when holding a piece. It pulls the energy field closer and has a grounding affect on the emotional bodies. It brings the astral body into the physical so could be very good for times when you need to concentrate. It almost feels like you have just had a cup of coffee.

Holding Empowerite does also make one feel brave. More energetic and stimulated to take action. This may be a good mineral to use with children diagnosed with hyperactivity or ADHD. Another use may be for times when you have ‘just one of those days’ you know the ones where you keep dropping things or walking into things. When your mind isn’t on the job so to speck. It will help to bring the mind back into the body. This is going to be an interesting mineral to trial and watch.', 'Libra', 'Root Chakra'),
  ('Enhydro Quartz', 'stone to balance the heart', 'Enhydro quartz, known for its internal water inclusions, is often associated with purity, life, and spiritual connection. It''s believed to represent the "elixir of life" and is used for cleansing, detoxification, and accessing the Akashic Records, a cosmic archive of spiritual information.', 'Pisces and Scorpio', 'heart and crown'),
  ('Epidote', 'stone of enchancing your current mood (good or bad)', 'Epidote is a strong enhancing stone and is one of the very few stones users should be cautious with when carrying it with them. Epidote will enhance anything, good or bad. If you are having a bad day and carrying Epidote on you, I would highly urge you to remove that piece and set it aside until you posses more positivity. However, if you are having a fantastic day filled with love, positivity, and happiness, Epidote is one stone that can really bring your mood higher than you may have thought was even possible. Just be cautious and deeply connected with yourself when working with this stone. Doing so, you’ll be able to notice even the most subtle of differences in yourself.', 'Gemini, virgo, Libra', 'all seven'),
  ('Epidote Dream Quartz', 'stone of peace', 'Epidote Dream Quartz from Madagascar.  It is a rejuvenation Quartz that helps one to come to terms with setbacks and loss. It aids recovery time after illness and breaks old patterns that cause restraint. A peaceful Quartz that is both calming and serene.  It is seen as a soul protector and gentle nurturer. A good crystal to have around you when you’re feeling a little lost or confused by life.


Healers also use if for helping those who have lost love ones.', 'Gemini , Pisces.', 'third eye, crown'),
  ('Epidote Quartz', 'stone for very restful sleep', 'Epidote Quartz Crystals are Quartz Crystals that have crystals of Epidote in and on them. The Epidote can be green, red/brown to black in color.', 'Gemini', 'Heart'),
  ('Etched Quartz', 'stone for to help you to gain access to healing information from the past', 'These crystals have etched surfaces. Etching can form in most varieties of Quartz. The etching is caused by water during the crystals growth cycle, or by mineral inclusions since dissolved away.', 'Aries', 'Third eye'),
  ('Eudialyte', 'Stone for purifying the blood', 'Eudialyte will give you more physical energy to help you achieve all your goals. It will act like a battery that adds energy to you when you’re not at your peak or at the top of your game.

Eudialyte is also a powerful protection stone that will keep the negative energies away. It will help you let go of pessimistic feelings as well.

When it comes to this stone, there will be no room in your life for pessimistic people, and you will steer clear of them when they threaten to come inside your circle.
Eudialyte is a strong grounding stone that will keep you balanced and aligned to your goals. It will fine tune the energies in your life and help you manifest your desires!

It will remind you of all the skills and talents that you possess and the many things that you can do with them.', 'Aries, Taurus, Scorpio', 'Heart'),
  ('Faden Quartz Crystal', '', 'Faden Quartz Crystals have white misty lines running through the center of them. They are most often formed from Clear Quartz and have tabular-style formation.', '', ''),
  ('Fancy Jasper', 'stone for grounding the stress energies', 'This opaque gemstone is available in mixes of green, red, lilac, mauve, brown and yellow colours. Very rarely in blue. Polished, it has a high sheen. Closely related to the Bloodstone, Fancy Jasper is a “supreme nurturer” that holds and supports during times of stress. This gemstone brings a sense of wellbeing by calming the mind and grounding the stress energies. 

Use palm stones to provide protection during Shamanic journeying. Place it in your  pillowcase for dream recall. Display in the home to absorb negative energies and to bring joy and tranquility. Carry it in your pocket to help clear your head and bring focus on any situation.', 'Aries, Scorpio', 'Root'),
  ('Fluorite', 'Stone of Cleansing And Stablisation', 'Fluorite absorbs and neutralises negative energy and stress.  An excellent learning aid, Fluorite increases our powers of concentration, self-confidence and helps us in decision-making.  It encourages positivity, balances the energies, and improves balance and coordination, both physically and mentally. Fluorite boosts the immune system and stimulates the regeneration and restructuring of cells and DNA, particularly in the skin and respiratory tract, and heals ulcers and wounds.  Fluorite strengthens bone tissue, and alleviates rheumatism, arthritis and spinal injuries.  It improves the discomfort of shingles and other nerve-related pain.', 'Pisces', 'third eye'),
  ('Fluorite – Blue', 'stone of  Uplifting, Invigorating, Calming', 'Blue Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from light to dark blue. This mineral is readily available.', 'Caprocorn, Pisces', 'Throat, Third Eye'),
  ('Fluorite – Clear White', 'stone of Calming Intuition  Osteoporosis', 'Clear White Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from clear to white. This mineral is readily available.', 'Pisces', 'Crown'),
  ('Fluorite – Gold', 'stone for  Stabilizing, Confidence', 'Gold Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from light to dark gold.', 'Pisces', 'Solar Plexus'),
  ('Fluorite – Green', 'stone of Uplifting, invigorating', 'Green Fluorite is a member of the Halides family.

This mineral comes in all sorts of shades of green, from light lime right through to deep emerald green.', 'Taurus, Libra', 'Heart'),
  ('Fluorite – Pink – Magenta', 'stone of  Calming, Love', 'Pink Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. It comes in crystalline Cluster form, with color ranging from light pink to magenta.', 'Pisces', 'Heart'),
  ('Fluorite – Purple', 'stone of  Uplifting, Mentally Stimulating', 'Purple Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. This mineral comes in all sorts of shades of purple, from light lilac right through to deep purple.', 'Capricorn, Aquarius, Pisces', 'Third Eye'),
  ('Fluorite – Rainbow', 'stone for Uplifting, Mentally Soothing, Balancing', 'Rainbow Fluorite is a member of the Halides family. As the name suggests, it comes in a rainbow of colors! It can also have flecks of Pyrite inside.', 'Capricorn, Aquarius, Pisces', 'Dependent on colors. Green-Heart, Gold-Solar Plexus, Blue-'),
  ('Fluorite Octahedron', 'stone of Calming, Love', 'Fluorite Octahedron is a member of the Halides family. It comes in cleaved crystalline form, in a wide variety of colors. This mineral is readily available.', 'Pisces', 'Dependant on Color'),
  ('Fossilwood', 'stone of access memory', 'From ancient times, anything that has fossilised holds the blueprint of what it once was. Fossilwood grew from seed, from something very tiny into something quite sizable and was nourished by the Earth Mother. The tree that the wood came from spent many years growing and remembering.



 
Many cycles of the seasons and many full moons. It is said that fossilised wood can help access memory. It can aid recall of past life memory. Very useful in the treatment of Alzheimer’s, Parkinson’s disease and incidents of traumatic shock. It can be used to dispel attachment to comfort patterns that are detrimental to future progress.

Fossilised wood needs to be kept in close contact with the skin in order for it to infiltrate the aura. Necklaces and bracelets would be ideal, or used as worry stones.', 'Capricorn, sagittarius, scorpio', 'Root , Third Eye Chakras'),
  ('Fuchsite', 'stone of Justice and balance', 'Fuchsite is the stone of rejuvenation and renewal.

When you feel like you’re stuck where you are and nothing significant is happening with your life, Fuchsite is a very good stone to have with you.

It will give you a fresh new perspective on life, and it will make you appreciate all the good things you have going for you.

This stone carries the energies and vitality of youth, and it will fill your life with joy, laughter, and playfulness.

It will give you a sense of excitement, and it will make you look forward to what lies ahead.

Fuchsite will show you how you can derive joy and satisfaction even from the little things. It will make you understand that happiness is not something that you just stumble upon on the street.

You are responsible for your own happiness. Happiness is what you make it! Fuchsite can help you restore the joy and happiness in your life.

It will not happen overnight, though.

But you will start to see the subtle difference in the way you feel about the small things, the way you speak to people who normally annoy you, and the way you respond to situations that usually make your blood boil.', 'Taurus, Libra', 'Heart'),
  ('Gabbro', 'stone of determination and speed', 'Similar too, and sometimes referred to as Mystic Merlinite, Gabbro is usually mined in Madagascar. This mineral is rich in magnesium and iron. It’s colours are usually blue/black/grey and mottled.


This crystal is used to help one understand and use their alter ego on the darker masculine side of their energy is a positive way.

When we need drive, determination and speed to achieve something, this is the crystal to ally ones energy with.

Kali energy would be associated with this crystal along with Lillith and Hectate. This is the mineral of the dark goddess.', 'Sagittarius)', 'throat chakra'),
  ('Gaia Stone', 'stone for grounding and nurturing', 'Believed to carry the heart chakra energy from the soul of the earth, this unusual glassy material derives from fresh volcanic ash and is believed to have mysterious energetic properties.



Gaia stone is ‘Green Obsidian’ and used for connecting to Mother Earth. Made from the earth and transformed through trauma and evolution, Gaia Stone helps to heal wounds from the past and aids transformations along ones spiritual path.

Although some think of Gaia Stone as very young, Mother Nature enhanced the stone and as such, it has much to offer energetically. It has the ability to pull you magnetically together and hold you. We have much to learn about this crystal but it is well worth experimenting with. Very good for grounding and nurturing. Sometimes referred to as the Earth Goddess Stone.

Usually found wire wrapped or silver wrapped.', 'Taurus, Virgo, Libra', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Galaxite', 'stone for enhancing the spiritual and mystical senses', 'Also known as Micro Labradorite, the opaque and very dark green colour of Galaxite sometimes appears black, with sparkly inclusions that make it appear as though one is gazing at a galaxy of stars. Galaxite is a form of Labradorite which carries an intense energy that is protecting, balancing, and cleansing of the Aura, an energy field around living things. It is believed that the Angels sent Galaxite to Earth to heal it. Its high vibrations stimulate the Crown Chakra and assists in contacting beings from other dimensions and planes. This crystal assists in intuitive growth, enhancing the spiritual and mystical senses. It is particularly beneficial and considered essential for those studying astrology, and those practicing astral travel and astral projection. Galaxite also carries a grounding energy, decreasing stress and anxieties. 

The healing energies of Galaxite include, being effective against colds and respiratory problems, stimulating the metabolism, helpful with digestive problems, stops energy leaks from the Aura, eases pain associated with rheumatism and gout. Wear Galaxite to increase feelings of joy, promote charisma and protect against depression. 

An excellent crystal for energy workers! Connects one to the source of Divine wisdom. Use the moonlight to energize.', 'All', 'Root, Crown, Soul Star'),
  ('Galena', 'stone of harmony', 'Galena is one of the ultimate grounding stones that exist. It has a very stimulating and balancing energy that can remove emotional blocks, and it will infuse you with a strong ‘can do’ attitude.

This stone will open your mind to new concepts. It will also absorb negative energies and convert them to useful and uplifting energies.

Galena will bring stability and security to areas of your life where there’s confusion, conflict, or overworked emotions.
It’s used to ground and center your energies, and it will harmoniously open new pathways to wisdom and enlightenment.

It will promote peace and harmony, and it will encourage you to be more loving, forgiving, and understanding.

Galena will enhance the power of other stones and crystals.', 'Capricorn', 'Root'),
  ('Garnet', 'Stone of grounding and manifesting', 'Garnet is able to tap energy, allowing it to empower any other crystals and one’s abilities. It can be used to add extra energy to any ritual or action, giving them a boost in power and effectiveness. It emotionally dispels negativity, worry, and panic; allowing one to face the truth of any situation and to move forward from emotional setbacks. Being directly related to the blood, Garnet is able to provide healthy regulation to the heart and blood flow. It supports the reproductive organs, providing them with oxygen and blood. It relieves skin conditions (especially inflammations), aids in spine disorders and supports the bones, cells, and lungs. Garnet is able to repair the RNA and DNA and empowers regeneration in general.', 'Aries, leo, virgo, capricorn and aquarius', 'Root'),
  ('Garnierite', 'stone of hope, calm and peace', 'Garnierite is a beautiful green mineral with light swirly bands of light green and white. This crystal makes one catch their breath. It makes the heart skip a beat and feels like ‘falling in love’; soft and fluttery. This is because it works on the emotions of love, teaching one to love themselves first.


There comes a time after the first encounters of emotional relationships that one begins to realise that the first step for a a balanced relationship is to learn to love themselves, flaws and all!

This crystal brings light into the heart chakra. It is the ‘Happy Crystal’, bringing hope, calm and peace.', 'Leo, Virgo', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Gaspeite', 'stone of manifestation', 'Gaspeite holds a very grounding energy that will provide strong vibrations to your chakras. It will boost your spiritual growth and enhance your visions.

This stone will develop your clairvoyant abilities and other psychic talents.

It’s also a very spiritual stone that can help in contacting or communicating with the spirit world.

It will bring you a grounded spiritual energy that will encourage you to live life realistically with a spiritual perspective.
It will encourage you to be more aware of how you should be living your life while focusing on the spiritual aspects of each situation.
When things take place in your life, you will be able to recognize what you need to do to make the necessary changes in your actions, emotions, and thoughts.

This stone has excellent metaphysical properties that will help you remove the clutter and the unnecessary noise and distractions.

It will give you a good plan of action that will help you change your life for the better.

Gaspeite will make you pay attention to the situations that are happening and are yet to unfold, and it will assist you in making the best move.

This stone will help you receive new information, boost your aptitude, and strengthen your discernment.', 'Virgo', 'Heart'),
  ('Generator Quartz', 'stone of  energy', 'In crystal healing, the clear quartz generator is a beacon of amplified energy—used to channel, meditate, and heal. Said to harmonize with the soul star chakra, it helps awaken the higher self. Clear quartz, the master healer, magnifies the power of other stones and brings light to all layers of being.', 'na', 'Crown Chakra and the Soul Star Chakra'),
  ('Glastonbury Coral', 'stone of self-love, passion and creativity', 'An exciting find around the wetlands of Glastonbury turned up some interesting pieces of stone. On closer inspection after cutting and later polishing it was discovered that the fossilised gemstone was part of an ancient coral reef.



Around one hundred and seventy million years ago the region which we now call the Mendips, was much warmer then today and part of a shallow tropical sea that stretched westwards into Pembrokeshire. These rich warm waters were home to our very own tropical coral reef.

This lucky find has given us some beautiful pieces of local coral to work with and it is always an amazing experience to work with crystals and minerals from sacred locations. Glastonbury is known as the heart chakra of the world and fossilised coral from around Glastonbury will have an amazing memory and energy to work with.

We are expecting Glastonbury Fossilised Coral to have a similar energy to Spiny Oyster Shell and other Corals from around the world. We will be looking to work with it on emotional sensitivities, psychic development, to be attentive to energy shifts and alert one to danger.

Coral is associated with Goddess energy and associated with the base chakra and the sacral chakra.

Red Coral is believed to absorb negative emotional energy and then like the tides of the sea of its birth clear, cleanse and wash it away. It transforms negatives to positives. It encourages self-love, passion and creativity.

All Coral is thought to aid depression due to its fantastic ability to transmute energy. It is used to calm emotions especially after trauma, when dealing with mental health issues and coping with grief.

Place a piece of Coral on your altar next to your altar candles to act as protection and alert you to danger of negative energies. Keep a piece of Coral on you to hold when feeling emotional stress and tension to calm you. Coral can aid tears to fall to clear stagnant energies or pent up grief. It can break up blockages of negativity in one’s aura allowing one to move on from the past.', 'na', 'heart chakra'),
  ('Goethite', 'stone for to holds the spiritual energies', 'Goethite is a stone that will help you form a deeper and more meaningful connection with the earth.

It’s a particularly good stone to have, especially if you have been affected by changes in your natural environment or surroundings.

It will support you in all manner so that you will feel safe and at home in your natural world.

This stone will also instill a deeper concern and sense of conservation when it comes to the environment.

Goethite is a very helpful stone that will help you heal your grief after you have lost someone you love.

Any feeling that you find tough to manage will be greatly eased with the help of this stone.

Whenever you feel choked up by your emotions and you no longer feel like you’re in control, Goethite will help you by allowing you to acknowledge and feel your emotions without breaking you apart.', 'Aries', 'third eye, Sacral, root'),
  ('Gold', 'stone of Joy, Calm, Self Esteem, Balance', 'Gold is a member of the Metallic family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from yellow to gold. This mineral is readily available, for a price', 'Leo', 'Crown, Heart'),
  ('Goldstone', 'Stone of inspiration', 'As a beautifully constructed form of glass, Goldstone represents the power and fire of ingenuity. While not coming naturally from the ground, Goldstone has a wonderfully magical history and spiritual meaning. Goldstone’s meaning is that of a stone of inspiration, and even a warrior stone, for its ability to transmute lofty ideas into physical manifestations of power. While coming in many colors, it’s most popular, and common variations are orange, reddish, and of course, gold. Flecks of iron glimmer underneath its shiny exterior and make a truly stunning appearance. The colors of orange, red, and gold all relate to the summer months where the sun is the highest in the sky, and the days are at their longest. Perhaps harkening back to its home of Italy, Goldstone provides a sense of rich warmth, the feeling of long beautiful sunsets dancing on brick walls, and fiery passions. Goldstone is an excellent stone to have with you when embarking on new journeys. It helps to ensure that you will have good fortune on your path and be met with fond adventure. It also goes by “Dell Roba” in some parts, meaning “charming” in Italian. If you wish to impress a suitor or lover, consider wearing a piece of Goldstone in your outfit and watch them be mesmerized with its beauty. Due to its reflective gaze, Goldstone is also a protector stone. Any stone which possesses a reflective sheen on its surface is perfect for repelling unwanted energies.', 'sagittarius', 'root'),
  ('Goshenite', 'stone of Calming, Guilt, Grief', 'Goshenite is a member of the Beryl family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from white to clear white. This mineral is readily available.', 'Cancer, Libra', 'Crown'),
  ('GRANDIDERITE', '', 'Grandiderite was first described in 1902 by French mineralogist Alfred Lacroix, who found it in Madagascar and named it in honor of the French explorer Alfred Grandidier, an expert on Madagascan natural history. This extremely rare blue-green mineral has been found in a number of places around the world, but so far only Madagascar and Sri Lanka have produced any gem-quality stones, and these are still extremely scant. The majority of the known stones are translucent, but the most rare, and therefore most valuable, example ever found was transparent. In fact, the stone was initially assumed to be another rare gem, serendibite, because grandiderite of that color and transparency had yet to be seen. The gem was only identified as grandiderite after expert analysis and was subsequently sold for an undisclosed sum. It’s safe to assume that if a gem of similar quality were to be unearthed, its scarcity alone would ensure it fetched an extremely high price.', '', 'throat'),
  ('Green adventurine', 'Stone of strength, confidence, courage and happiness', 'Green Aventurine provides strength, confidence, courage, and happiness. It renews one’s optimism for life and pushes us to take action to acquire what we want in this world. This stone urges one to get out of their comfort zone and take on new opportunities. Allow this stone to take you on an adventure and help you grow as an individual. Green Aventurine is here to keep your emotional body calm when trying things that may be uncomfortable at first. Those nervous butterflies in your stomach will be replaced by an ever-burning fire that is eager to burn. This crystal is here to help you enjoy life while sharing your energy and experiences with those closest to you. Your friends will begin to see the changes you’ve made and be motivated to follow your approach. This will cause a chain reaction of positivity that will change both your life and those who you love most.', 'aries leo', 'heart'),
  ('Green Chalcedony', 'stone for enhance insight, to calm the mind', 'A quartz of courage, Green Chalcedony inspires one by instilling the soul with strength. Use it to enhance insight, to calm the mind, to release anxiety. Green Chalcedony is also a very protective stone and can be used as an amulet or a talisman to ward off low vibrating energies and bad vibes. With its green tree colour, Chalcedony will increase your brain power; let it charge and stimulate your mind like a tree growing with light and water. It strengthens the mind and makes it easier to deal with hard issues.

Bright Green Chalcedony promotes growth, love, empathy, self-growth and forgiveness. Improves emotional health, promotes "joie de vivre”. Thightly linked to the Heart Chakra, it is a stone of excellence for healing the heart by clearing the stale energies and instilling self-love.   

Carry it in your bra, in your pocket, place in your pillowcase or crystal grid to attract love and healing energies into your heart and your home.', 'Cancer, Virgo, Sagittarius, Aquarius', 'Solar Plexus, Heart, Throat'),
  ('Green Fluorite', 'Stone of longevity, nourishment, rejuvenation and new Beginnings', 'Green Fluorite is an amazing auric cleanser. Use it in clockwise circular motions above and around the body to cleanse the aura. It is as if a fresh breath of nature’s air breezes over and through your body!

Green Fluorite helps with cellular healing and regeneration, especially when used in conjunction with Purple Fluorite. It also has exceptional anti-cancer properties.

On an emotional level – Green Fluorite has very strong anti addiction properties. It helps give one both the emotional and physical fortitude to beat the cravings and helps one break through the patterns of repetition.

At an intellectual level – Green Fluorite helps one to think through feelings and make good speedy decisions while under pressure. This beautiful crystal inspires original thoughts that are both creative and at the same time practical.

Green Fluorite helps one ground nature’s spiritual energy into the physical body, particularly when used in elixir form. One may also use the Green Fluorite elixir for gardening uses, such as adding to water to nourish the plants. It may also be put in spray bottles to be used as an aura cleanser for both yourself and your environment – working at both the physical, and spiritual levels.

Green Fluorite is a wonderful gardening companion. Pop one in your pocket and your intuitive processes will let you know just what to do – your gardens will positively thrive with this approach!', 'Taurus, Libra', 'Heart'),
  ('Green Garnet', 'stone for bring courage and hope', 'Garnet comes in a variety of colours, red, green, yellow, orange, brown, pink, purple, gray and black. Used as a protective talisman against negative energy. Associated with the Heart Chakra, it is considered a love magnet. 

Green Garnet is beneficial in awaking the kundalini energy, a hidden force holding all human potential in your body. It is an energizing stone, bestowing passion and determination to accomplish your goals. Green Garnet revitalises, purifies and balances energy. It is said to relieve emotional conflict, activate and strengthen survival instincts, bring courage and hope.', 'Aries', 'Heart'),
  ('Green Goldstone', 'stone for pain relief, heals angina, reduces inflammation, enhances eye sight.', 'A man-made stone from chromium, Green Goldstone is associated with the Heart Chakra as is especially good for emotional healing. Helps connect to the Divine and imparts wisdom, energy and courage. Green Goldstone guards against unwanted energies, protects against psychic attacks, protects from diseases of the skeletal system (great for arthritic sufferers), and protects sensitive empaths. The Green Goldstone also supports abundance. 

Some of the healing properties of Green Goldstone include; pain relief, heals angina, reduces inflammation, enhances eye sight.', 'Sagittarius, Taurus', 'Heart'),
  ('Green Kyanite', 'stone of protection', 'Green Kyanite, is found in Pakistan, it is a rarer form of Kyanite, it is a very powerful energy conductor. It has the ability to align all the Chakras and clears the energy meridians without conscious effort. It also has the ability to absorb and then dispel negative energy and therefore, never needs to be cleansed. Kyanite is a high vibrating gemstone, and because its vibrations are so high, it eliminates low vibrations.  Low vibrations that are side-effects of grief, anxiety, fear, loss, and abuse. The vibration of this gemstone is so powerful that it eliminates these low vibrating energies of anyone nearby. It will also stimulate higher states of wellness and wellbeing. It places a shield around the wearer and protects her/him from their surroundings. An excellent gemstone to use for mourning. Kyanite allows us to let go. This benefits letting go of the pass and bad or low vibrating energies associated with those memories. 

Wear Green Kyanite for protection during astral projection or travel and shamanic journeys. Stimulates the Third Eye, telepathy, intuition, the higher mind and lucid dreaming. Place inside or grid your home to keep the positive energies high and eliminate the lower energies. Place by your bedside or in your pillowcase to protect you during sleep and stimulate lucid dreams. Wear to protect yourself at work or during travel. Place on the forehead to stimulate inner-visions. Place on the throat to trigger inner-truth and stimulate communication.

Green Kyanite aligns all the Chakras, restores energy balance and aligns the meridians. Builds telepathic bridge between two people. Creates a bridge to connect to higher dimensions and reinforces the protective shield around the Aura. Helps develop psychic power, intuition, and telepathy. Due to its high vibrations, it is a natural pain reliever (pain being a low vibrating energy, high energy elim', 'Aries, Taurus, Leo, Pisces', 'All'),
  ('Green Obsidian', 'stone for cleansing and stimulating', 'Most Green Obsidian is man made, in China, from glass. All glass comes from sand, that comes from the earth. There has been a lot of controversy around man made gemstones, however, it still has energy, it still has vibrations.

However, there is a natural Green Obsidian that is found in Northern California, USA. It is rarer and more expensive. Here we talk about the man made Green Obsidian for the natural look under Natural Green Obsidian.

Green Obsidian is cleansing and stimulating, it works on the Heart Chakra, helping to purge the Heart of any emotional junk. Assists in not repeating patterns in one’s life path, clearing the way for spiritual growth. 

Green Obsidian is a wonderful gemstone that acts as a shield against negativity energy and guarding against blockages that form in your spiritual journey. Green Obsidian is an Earthen stone that resonates with the Earthen Element and will help you find proper grounding for meditation. This stone stimulates your higher consciousness and helps you achieve deeper thought; which can aid in paths of enlightenment. Working with Green Obsidian will help you dissolve blockages that form through negative energy and negative thoughts, and encourages you to find your way. Green Obsidian is also known as Gaia Stone. It is a see-through stone with a leafy-green colour.', 'Gemini', 'Heart'),
  ('Guardianite', 'Stone for infusion of life force, grounding, strength, protection', 'Guardianite brings a deep and immediate grounding through the root chakra. It offers an instantaneous connection with the Earth and its upwelling life force. As Guardianite’s currents flow into one’s field, they permeate the Liquid Crystal Body Matrix with a humming vibration of well-being. Guardianite makes one feel happy, calm and safe. It nourishes the etheric and astral bodies, enhancing their integration with the physical self.', 'All', 'Root'),
  ('Hackmanite', 'stone for self-love, self-trust and conviction of ones beliefs', 'Hackmanite is natural sodalite but what makes it different from our usual beloved sodalite is a rather unique fluorescence quality about it. Usually we only see varieties like this from Afghan and Burma with little on the market. Because of this little has been documented of it’s energy properties from natural healers.


It is believed to stimulate the throat, third eye and crown chakra bringing confidence, logic and reason. This would be a great crystal for those requiring a boost in confidence in the field of the performing arts of all kinds, for public specking or simply for interviews or exams.

Used for meditation Hackmanite aids self worth and confidence in ones ability. It teaches one self-love, self-trust and conviction of ones beliefs. It is this quality that gives it its place in this week’s crystals because the whole topic of Lemuria is subjective. For those channeling new or undocumented information it can be a little unnerving to disclose to others a new found revelation. Working with Hackmanite we believe will help one assimilate information brought through from ones spiritual and psychic channeling.', 'Sagittarius', 'crown, third eye'),
  ('Halite', 'stone of Confidence', 'Halite is a member of the Halide family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, displaying many colors. This mineral is readily available.', 'Cancer, Pisces', 'Heart'),
  ('Hanksite', 'Stone for to helps to cleanse and clear your entire spiritual body', 'Hanksite it the ultimate cleansing and purification mineral. It clears both the physical and energetic bodies, and works on every level and dimension.

Holding it in meditation, it will begin by focussing on and cleansing the chakras that are most in need, removing any blockages that are impeding flow, and activating and aligning the entire chakra system, and may also clear and balance blockages between male/female or physical/spiritual characteristics of self. It then works outwards, cleansing and clearing interdimensional aspects of the chakras and on to the subtle bodies. Once all layers are clear, it may repeat the process, working at a deeper level. The end result leaves the user feeling not only purified, but also energised and whole, with the energetic body more homogenous with the physical.

In addition, Hanksite raises our vibration, creating a “lightness of being”, and making it an excellent mineral for “rewiring” ourselves to the current energies. It can also be useful in astral travel and interdimensional work. Melody recommends it to help us to understanding death before experiencing it.', 'Taurus', 'Crown; affects all chakras'),
  ('Healerite', 'stone of profound healing energy', 'Healerite is a newly found crystal with an amazing gentle vibration. It is a powerful healing stone and can heal on a cellular level. Healerite instill hope and provides a sense of faith in all things. It brings forth self-love and allows one to look at themselves with acceptance and complete compassion. Healerite is a stone of balance and will help align and re-energize chakras as well as the bodies meridians. Increases stability emotionally as well as eternally. Healerite will enable you to do soul intervention and clean all emotional stuck bonds. Healerite is connected to the earth and will help open the door to feel and balance with her energy. Healerite brings forth love and joy and helps to heal pain from past lives.', 'Taurus', 'heart, solar plexus'),
  ('Heliodor', 'stone of Balance', 'Heliodor is a member of the Beryl family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from yellow to deep gold. This mineral is readily available.', 'Leo', 'Solar Plexus'),
  ('Hematite', 'Stone of grounding and stability', 'Hematite focuses energy and emotions for balance between the body, mind and spirit. Dissolves negativity and prevents you from absorbing the negativity of others. Haematite is strong, supporting timidity, boosting self-esteem and survivability, enhancing willpower and reliability, and imparting confidence.', 'Aquarius', 'Root'),
  ('Hematite, Rainbow', 'stone for grounding, calming', 'Shiny black Hematite contains grounding energies. This type of hematite is coated with a titanium aura, reflecting all the colours of the rainbow. It''s the perfect mineral to quiet the mind. Use during meditation to enter a higher state of consciousness. It repels negative thoughts from your mind and clears your aura of all negativity. Assist health issues related to high blood pressure or hyperactive disorders. It relieves insomnia, calms the muscles and balances the nervous system. Especially good for people with an overactive mind who can''t sleep at night. 

To prevent pressure built up in the ears during air travel, keep a piece in each pocket.  In Feng Shui, Hematite is used for its grounding, calming, as well as protective properties. Place in your car, at your office computer, or in your purse to help with a burst of strong and cool, calming energy. Place by the front door of your home for good Feng Shui, on the North side of your home for the career and life path energy, or in the West of your home for creativity energy.', 'Taurus, Capricorn', 'Root, All'),
  ('Hemimorphite', 'stone of self expression and communication', 'Hemimorphite is a gentle healing crystal bringing angelic healing to the troubled mind. For those who ‘think too much’; whose brain feels like it is running on overdrive constantly.



This mineral when held sends out a signal to the angelic realm that someone requires a little help right now. This light, no matter how dim it appears on the physical plane, shine bright in the angelic realm and is easily followed right back to you.

Your angels will draw near and hold you whilst you go through troubled times; during operations, hospital stays, pregnancy and birth. For all those times when you need comfort, this crystal delivers.

Simply hold a piece in your hand, wire wrap a piece to wear or keep in your pocket. When required, hold and send out that thought of ‘help’ and your angels will come.', 'Libra', 'Crown'),
  ('Herkimer Diamond', 'Stone of Attunement', 'Being doubly terminated, Herkimer Diamonds have the ability to not only transmit their own energies, but to receive spiritual energy and to amplify and focus it intently. They are reported to be harder than all other Quartz. What they lack in physical size, they more than make up for in spirit energy. It has the abilitiy to receive and magnify the influence of other stones, along with being programmed for love, well-being and healing.', 'Aries, sagittarius', 'Crown, third eye'),
  ('Heulandite', 'stone of Uplifting', 'Heulandite is a member of the Zeolites family. It comes in both massive and crystalline form, with color ranging from white, green and peach. This mineral is readily available.', 'Aries', 'Crown'),
  ('Heulandite, Green', 'Stone to stimulate your brain and improve mental clarity', 'Heulandite will promote an altered state of awareness and assist you in accessing and visualizing ancient knowledge.

It will also help you access your Akashic records.
This stone will show you how you can unlock the inherent messages of your dreams and activate the portals to interdimensional reality.

It will unlock the connection between your heart and your head, helping you become more centered and uplifted while easing your emotional burdens.
Heulandite will calm the mind and promote meditative states to open yourself up to divine guidance.', 'Sagittarius', 'heart, solar plexus'),
  ('Hiddenite', 'stone of  joy and happiness', 'Hiddenite in its gem quality state is somewhat a collectors item due to its rarity.



Hiddenite is from the family of Kunsite and belongs to the spodumene group of minerals. Coloured by chromium oxide Hiddenite can appear almost clear when seen at one angle and light green to yellowish green from another. It deceives you in different lighting by playing games with you. You think you know it and then it surprises you.

This crystal is little used in healing as it is a bit of a new comer but believed to bring joy and happiness. To give one confidence to dance and express their inner child.

Valued by shamanic healers usually by swooping minerals Hiddenite is used to heal great emotional trauma, to aid the healing of mental health and to cushion the delivery of shock news. It is making a name for itself for use with addictions and healing those recovering from abuse.

Natural Hiddenite is raw and fractured. It forms in rough crystalline structures with a translucent hint of colour. In this form it has a delicate kind of beauty and teaches one to love thyself first with all ones idiosyncrasies, crazy ideas and eccentricity. To value uniqueness and individuality as a prized possession and a gift.', 'All', 'Heart Chakra'),
  ('Himalayan Quartz', 'stone to help with chronic fatigue, depression, and anxiety, as well as physical ailments such as migraines, muscle pain, and respiratory issues.', 'Himalayan Quartz is a crystal of legend, cradled in the ancient arms of the sacred Himalayas and infused with their timeless, celestial energy. It is said to whisper the wisdom of the mountains and the stars, holding a revered place among those who walk the path of spirit. Mystics and seekers treasure its radiant presence for the clarity it brings, the veil it lifts, and the deep stillness it awakens within. Through meditation and quiet communion, Himalayan Quartz becomes a portal—opening the heart, expanding awareness, and connecting the soul to higher realms. In this article, we will journey into the mystical origins of Himalayan Quartz, explore its healing powers, uncover sacred cleansing rituals, and reflect on its spiritual essence beyond the stars.', 'Aquarius and Scorpio', 'crown chakra'),
  ('Horn Coral', 'stone of  Eases Depression, Emotional Balance', 'This particular ancient Coral reef strangely enough now is situated thousands of feet up in the Utah mountains. The rare red Horn Coral would have been considered a treasure to the Native American Shaman who would travelled far and wide to collect or trade this hidden gem. There appears to be no mining for this Coral now except a few prospectors picking over the area and occasional finds.

This particular ancient Coral reef strangely enough now is situated thousands of feet up in the Utah mountains. The rare red Horn Coral would have been considered a treasure to the Native American Shaman who would travelled far and wide to collect or trade this hidden gem. There appears to be no mining for this Coral now except a few prospectors picking over the area and occasional finds.

Read More

Horn Coral gets its name from the way the Coral formed. Think of it like the branches or roots of a tree or horns of a stag. Over millions of years the natural original organic material has been replaced by minerals that give the Coral Agate its now beautiful colour.

Used as a lucky charm worn around the neck to attract good fortune. Red Horned Coral is worn as a sign of respect for the Goddess and although a water element it’s colour denotes fire, passion, fertility and inspiration. The Sharman would recommend the women elders to wear Horn Coral to aid the working together and co-operation of the tribe.

Native Americans believe this to be an important stone for them and would treat it with respect. It is quite rare and not always available so this adds to its allure and value.

We believe that the red Horn Coral from Utah was considered a very spiritual stone for a nation to posses. It is said that it would have been used in ceremony to bring cohesion of the tribe, it would adorn the handle or be the handle of the talking stick. It would have been used in sacred divine ceremonies to protect and bring fertility to the woman, protect the young women approaching puberty and aid prophetic visions in dream walking. This is a stone of mystery and magic, of bygone shamanic workings and of rediscovery in the wisdom of our ancestors.

